• Regular building competitions, with rewards!  
• Fun filled games with rewards (Colour Madness, Mazes, Parkour, Replicator, Spleef, Last Man Standing, Survival Games, Infection, Capture the Flag, Skywars, Fishing, Blockhunt, Build Battle, Walls, Murder Mystery, Boost, Village Defence and Party Games!)  
• Fully automated Survival Games  
• Incredible Prison server with bonuses, hidden secrets and challenges  
• Original SkyBlock with teams, custom generators, challenges and greenhoueses.  
• Skygrid world with a Nether and End grid!  
• Economy, Jobs and Player Markets.  
• Creative Plots world with customisable weather, time and effects.  
• Community Parkour world to build and challenge your friends.  
• Separate PVP and PVE hardcore worlds to challenge yourself!  
• LWC protection (chests, doors, dispensers, etc)  
• NO PVP, except in PVP designated areas and games.  
• Hack/cheat detection - Cheaters are not welcome here!', 'play.addstarmc.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.addstarmc.com/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'minecraft-middle-earth', 'Minecraft Middle-Earth', 'Minecraft Middle-Earth is an ambitious project to recreate the imagined world of J.R.R. Tolkien.  
  
