INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'genuinemc-semi-vanilla-1-21-11', 'GenuineMC [Semi-Vanilla ~ 1.21.11]', '**Welcome to GenuineMC!  
A Semi-Vanilla Minecraft Server  
_Established: July 8th, 2013_**
  

**Who are we?**
GenuineMC is a Semi‑Vanilla Minecraft server built by an incredible community of players. Over the 11 years of operation, people of all ages, backgrounds, and nationalities have found their home here. Their ideas and passions have helped guide our journey and keep our blocky world afloat for many years!   
From day one, our team has focused on creating a place where everyone feels welcome, regardless of whether you are brand new or have been with us since the beginning. We listen to your thoughts, appreciate your stories, and genuinely value your feedback. Every suggestion, every comment, and every shared experience helps us make GenuineMC an amazing place to play.   
We’re proud of the world we’ve built together, and we’re excited to continue shaping its future with you.  
  

**What Does “Semi‑Vanilla” Mean on GenuineMC?**
At GenuineMC, “Semi‑Vanilla” means staying true to the core Minecraft experience while enhancing the game with carefully selected improvements that respect its original design. Our goal is to preserve everything players already love about Vanilla Minecraft, while taking into account the quality of life improvements our community wants to see.   
We use a combination of plugins and custom datapacks to enhance gameplay in ways that feel intuitive, not intrusive. These additions never overshadow the foundation of Minecraft itself. In fact, you can log in and play without relying on any of our enhancements and still enjoy the classic survival experience exactly as intended.  
So, what are you waiting for? Come build, explore, and make memories with us at **SemiVanilla.Genmc.net** , a truly genuine Minecraft community built By Players For Players!   
  

Want to meet the community first or stay connected outside the game? Join us on Discord at **https://discord.gg/XT7FSxw4uV**  
We’d love to welcome you in!
  

  
© 2023–2026 GenuineMC, LLC. All rights reserved.  
All Minecraft-related content and materials are trademarks and copyrights of Mojang AB or its licensors.  
**NOT AN OFFICIAL MINECRAFT PRODUCT. NOT APPROVED BY OR ASSOCIATED WITH MOJANG.**  
The GenuineMC server and services are independently owned and operated by GenuineMC, LLC and are not affiliated with Mojang AB, Microsoft, or any related entity.', 'SemiVanilla.GenMC.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://linksta.cc/@genuinemc', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'sky-servers-survival-australian-survival-minecraft', 'Sky Servers Survival - Australian Survival Minecraft', 'WELCOME to SKY SERVERS SURVIVAL   
  
Established in 2012, Sky Servers is an Australian Survival Server.  
Hosted in Melbourne on our own dedicated server we offer a unique survival experience for all ages! We have a fantastic community of people from all over the world who help make SS amazing. The server is EULA compliant meaning no pay 2 win perks!   
  
CUSTOM PLUGINS   
  
Our developers work hard at developing unique content   
Each month we release cool updates to the server bringing in new gameplay options and improving the entire experience. Plugins like our custom market to easily buy and sell items and SkyRunes, our unique rune and custom enchantment system, are just some examples which improve the gameplay!   
  
MASSIVE MONTHLY EVENTS   
  
Each month we have a theme for build comps & events!   
Not only do we have a massive events weekend each month but we also have loads of spontaneous events each day! These include spleef, zombies, musical chairs and more. The End is reset frequently so that you can hunt the ender dragon and more!   
  
JOIN TODAY   
  
Get started on Sky Servers Survival!   
Website: [www.skyservers.net](https://www.skyservers.net%20)   
IP: sky-mc.net', 'sky-mc.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://www.skyservers.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'manacube', 'ManaCube', 'ManaCube is a flourishing minecraft community renowned for its wide variety of engaging Minecraft servers. Our unique take on game modes has been played by 5 million people over the last 11 years.  
  
Parkour  
• Complete over 2500 unique parkour maps and adventure maps  
  
Olympus  
• Greek mythology RPG, where you can grow as demi-gods through unique quests, mining, battles and exploration.  
  
Skyblock  
• Build your world on a secluded island. Explore other worlds for upgrades and items.  
  
Survival  
• A super enhanced Minecraft survival experience  
  
Factions  
• 1.21 base building/defending game where you use custom Raid & Defender mobs.  
  
Earth  
• Geopolitical sandbox experience, allowing players to create and rule their own towns or nations. The map is a re-creation of the Earth using satelite images.  
  
KitPvP  
• A classic 1.8 PVP server with a first-class anticheat  
  
Creative  
• Let your imagination run wild with unlimited resources and building tools to create anything you desire  
  
  
ManaCube is distinguished by its unique features. Cubits, the global in-game currency, can be earned and spent across all servers, adding an extra layer of depth to the economy. The Season Vault allows players to store immortal items that never reset, providing a sense of accomplishment and progression throughout different seasons.  
  
The networks resource pack enhances experiences with custom item models, unique monsters, cosmetics, menus, bosses and more! This customization brings a unique feel and look to ManaCube.  
  
Staff-hosted community events, as well as daily automated events to keep everyone engaged and offer plenty of opportunities to win Cubits and other exclusive prizes.  
  
In essence, ManaCube is more than just a minecraft server; it''s an ever-evolving, vibrant online community that continually offers an fun and immersive Minecraft experience.', 'lobby.manacube.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://manacube.com/play', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'cubecraft-games', 'CubeCraft Games', 'CubeCraft Games is one of the largest server networks in the world. We always strive to make the best games and bring the most fun to everyone. Our servers run 24/7 and have the capability to hold many thousands of players simultaneously. We have amazing support and a selection of games that you''ll never get bored of. A few of them include:  
