Hope to see you online!!!', 'play.cubecraft.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, '[http://www.cubecraft.net](https://www.cubecraft.net)', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'miragecraft-pixelmon-reforged', 'MirageCraft Pixelmon Reforged', 'Server IP: mc.miragecraft.net  
Website: [https://miragecraft.net](https://miragecraft.net/portal)  
Discord: [http://discord.gg/miragecraft](https://discord.gg/miragecraft)  
