Join us today and unleash your gaming potential amidst a world of limitless possibilities!', 'mp.extremecraft.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://www.extremecraft.net/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
