INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'project-eden', 'Project Eden', 'Welcome to Project Eden! A family-friendly, mature, and close-knit survival server with tons of fun things to do!   
  
We hold vanilla survival close to our hearts but we provide a lot of ''quality of life'' plugins to make playing a little easier and simpler. We also have mcMMO, a plugin that allows you to level skills such as mining, archery, and herbalism, but we have modified mcMMO from it''s default configuration to preserve the original survival concept.   
  
We provide a safe-space for you to accomplish whatever dream you have, whether it is building something spectacular, becoming the richest player, or making new friends.   
  
Our staff team works hard every day to make Project Eden a fun place for everyone and to assist you with any problems you may have. A staff member is almost always just a command away no matter what time of day, and we will always be glad to hop on to help you, whether you just have a question about how the server works or need grief fixed.   
  
As a community driven server, we use multiple different applications to stay in touch with our friends on the server, most notably Discord. If you are familiar with discord, feel free to join our discord server. If you are not familiar with discord, you can use the command /discord ingame to find a short description of the application.   
  
With custom plugins, an in-depth wiki, and our future custom achievement plugin, there are tons of features to help enhance your player experience. Be sure to check out our weekly minigame nights for members on Saturdays at 4 eastern, as well as server-wide holiday events! What are you waiting for?!   
![](https://i.imgur.com/oJbSOi9.png).', 'mcmp.projecteden.gg', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://projecteden.gg', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'pottercraft-mc', 'PotterCraft MC', '✨Explore the Magic on PotterCraft MC! ✨  
  
Step into the enchanting world of PotterCraft MC and immerse yourself in our carefully crafted replicas of Hogwarts, Durmstrang, Diagon Alley, and other iconic locations - all whilst learning spells, attending classes, embarking on quests, and participating in the wizarding world!  
In the survival world, you can engage in duels, form alliances, and establish your own community together with Towny! Alternatively, you can go solo and chill out on your own private housing plot - the choice is yours!  
  
Features:  
🏰 Detailed replicas of Hogwarts and other iconic Harry Potter locations  
📖 Spell learning, classes, and quests  
⚔ PvP battles & Duelling  
🌍 Towny and Runecraft for community building  
🦉 Customizable pets  
  
🔮 Visit https://pottercraftmc.com, and join the magic today!', 'play.pottercraftmc.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://pottercraftmc.com', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'minecrafters-mcers', 'Minecrafters (Mcers)', '¡Bienvenido a **Minecrafters**!
  
Si buscas un servidor tranquilo y amigable para jugar con tus amigos o conocer otros nuevos, ¡este es tu sitio!  
Disponemos de un servidor **survival vanilla** para disfrutar al completo la experiencia del juego. En este servidor se pueden construir proyectos de grandes construcciones y visitar los creados por el resto de usuarios; también se organizan eventos variados. Este servidor cuenta con un mapa para obtener recursos y otro con plots en creativo por si quieres desarrollar tus ideas antes de plasmarlas en el survival.  
También puedes jugar en nuestro **servidor de mods** , cuyo modpack cambia cada 3-4 meses. Más información en el [foro](https://mcers.es/mods).  
  
El [**foro**](https://foro.mcers.es) es el lugar en el que podrás resolver tus dudas, presentar proyectos e informarte de cambios en el servidor y eventos, entre otras muchas cosas que puedes descubrir.   
  
Tenemos un **servidor de[Discord](https://mcers.es/discord)** en el que puedes conocer a la comunidad, que no solo juega Minecraft; sino otros juegos que pueden ser de tu interés y conocer gente nueva con la que compartir tu tiempo libre.   
  
En esta comunidad nos centramos en el compañerismo, el buen ambiente y sobre todo en disfrutar de nuestra excelente comunidad.  
  
¡Esperamos verte pronto!', 'vip.mcers.es', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://mcers.es/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'villagercraft', 'VillagerCraft', 'VillagerCraft is een Nederlandstalige familie vriendelijke survival server.  
  
Wij updaten altijd naar de laatste minecraft versie zodat je van de nieuwste updates kunt genieten.  
  
De server beschikt over een anti-cheat en anti-grief plugin, zo doen onze creepers geen block-damage en kun je je projecten claimen door middel van claimblocks. Griefen of het gebruiken van hacks is streng verboden. Het is een leuke en gezellige community met een actief staff team die ook te bereiken is via discord.  
  
Een kleine opsomming van wat we te bieden hebben en wat ons uniek maakt:  
  
- Er zijn veel gratis ranks te verdienen, die je kan behalen door actief te spelen en te voten.  
- Schilder je eigen pixel schilderijen op canvas, ja echt. Het is mogelijk.  
- Bewerk armorstands ter decoratie voor je projecten en breng je project tot leven.  
- Elk weekend zijn er twee Happy Hours waarin je MMO Skills en economie bonussen krijgt.  
- Geen PvP, dus een veilige en relaxte omgeving voor na school of je werk.  
- Custom armor sets en wapens te verkrijgen via vote crates en andere systemen.  
- Behaal chat badges door verschillende milestones of achievements te behalen.  
- De server draait geheel op een speler-gebaseerde economie.  
- Er zijn regelmatig evenementen rondom feestdagen en verjaardagen.  
- De difficulty staat op HARD.  
  
Inmiddels bestaan we ruim 10 jaar op de markt en de server wordt actief onderhouden.  
  
We hopen dat je veel speel plezier zal hebben bij VillagerCraft.', 'play.villagercraft.nl:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.villagercraft.nl/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'clownercraft-puresurvival', 'ClownerCraft: PureSurvival', 'PureSurvival is the simplest server in the ClownerCraft Network.  
Literally, it''s survival. Thats pretty much all you need to know.  
  
This server has proved to be refreshing after playing other servers, especially from servers that give somewhat game changing permissions/commands. It''s a Non-PVP and No Grief server, Our staff are regularly online and will repair any griefing and ban those who cause problems!  
  
We do offer some aesthetic commands and permissions for paid ranks, if you wish to support the server.  
  
We also have a series of minigames and other servers in our network, accessible via our hub server (/hub).', 'pure.clownercraft.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://clownercraft.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'ardania-dein-freebuild-survival-server', '⛏Ardania - Dein Freebuild/Survival Server', '![](https://ardania.de/gallery/1_19_06_16_4_31_40.png)  
  
**Hallo liebe Minecraft Community,**   
  
Ardania ist ein kostenfreier Minecraftserver mit freundlicher Community und langer Tradition.  
Die früheste Serverversion entstand bereits Anfang 2011 und erlebte seither kontinuierliche Veränderung und Entwicklung.  
  
Im Gegensatz zu den großen Servernetzwerken mit hunderten von unbekannten Spielern und einem gesichtslosen Serverteam,  
erlebst du bei uns die klassische Minecraft Multiplayer Erfahrung. Mit Leuten die du bei jedem Login wieder siehst und einem Team,  
das offen und unbezwungen mit der Community zusammen spielt.  
  
  
🐲 **Was hat Ardania zu bieten?** 🐲  
  
〜➤ Zwei Bauwelten (Oberwelt und Nether)   
  
〜➤ Farmwelten (Nether, End und Normal)  
  
〜➤ Währungssystem, Jobs/Berufe und Shops  
  
〜➤ Ein Aufstiegssystem mit Neuling, Spieler & Stammi  
  
〜➤ Homepunkte, Spielerportale, Gildenportale und Weltenhub  
  
〜➤ Eine Eventwelt mit einigen Minigames wie Mobarena, Spleef u.a.  
  
〜➤ Eine Dungeon-Welt mit verschiedenen Instanzen  
  
〜➤ Eine PvP-Welt, sowie eine Jump''N''Run-Welt  
  
〜➤ Kreativ-Bauwelt, Pixelartwelt und Baukonteste   
  
〜➤ Weitere Features wie Hochzeiten, Gilden, Dekoköpfe, Achievements und vieles mehr!  
  
  
🌟 **Besonderheiten:** 🌟  
  
〜➤ Der Zugang zum Server ist kostenlos (Nur Premium, keine Cracked Accounts)  
  
〜➤ Neue Spieler erhalten ein Starterkit sowie Startgeld  
  
〜➤ **Keine VIP Ränge mit kaufbaren Spielervorteilen**   
  
〜➤ Unsere Bauwelt wird nicht resettet, nur die Minenwelten  
  
〜➤ Grundstücke werden selbst bei längerer Inaktivität nicht sofort entfernt.  
  
〜➤ Jedes Grundstück wird auf einzelne Spieler „protected“ (Blöcke, Truhen, Tiere, etc)  
  
〜➤ Die Größe der Spielergrundstücke im Freebuild ist praktisch unbegrenzt und kostenfrei  
  
  
📖 **Kontakte:** 📖  
  
Minecraft-Serveradresse: _**Server.Ardania.de**_  
_(Erreichbar mit Java und Bedrock Version)_  
  
Forum:**_Ardania.de_**  
Discord: **_Discord.Ardania.de_**  
_**Server-Trailer:[Hier Klicken!](http://bit.ly/ArdaniaTrailer)**_  
  
  
![](https://ardania.de/gallery/1_19_06_16_8_06_11.jpeg)', 'server.ardania.de', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.ardania.de', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'massivecraft', 'MassiveCraft', 'MassiveCraft is the Original Factions Server! Our server features Factions, PvP, Roleplay, Quests, and Minigames. Experience 30+ custom plug-ins, explore handcrafted worlds, and take part in an international community! Our server can be joined using 1.13–1.19.3 clients. Come and create your legacy!  
  
Factions, Kingdoms, and Sieges: Ever since the Factions plugin was created on MassiveCraft, it has constantly evolved and now boasts custom features, rank creation capabilities, and unique permissions! We now have 2 in-house extension plugins, Kingdoms and Sieges, which function as the Factions equivalent to Towny Nations. Group up together with your faction allies to form a Kingdom, and Siege your enemies to absorb their factions!   
  
PvP: Fight fierce McMMO enhanced battles, unlock and use special abilities with the custom MassiveRaces plug-in, and fight your heart out across a range of custom arenas using MCDuels KitPvP. Fulfill your destiny and become a PvP champion with our global ELO system! Take your fights to the battlefield with Kingdoms and Sieges!  
  
Roleplay: Aloria is MassiveCraft’s high fantasy setting. The City of Regalia is sprawling and contains the Regalian Empire’s brightest minds and lowest criminals. You can join guard charters, criminal gangs, noble families, businesses and more, all depending on how you wish to play your character! This city evolves based on the actions of players like you, so come and create your own stories!  
  
Events & Minigames: Our staff team works hard to make the server fun for each group of players and what they enjoy! We regularly host events and contests and have introduced Minigames. Fight across five custom PvP maps and fight together with your team to claim victory!  
  
Staff: Our friendly staff team is always here to help! Not only does MassiveCraft use an intuitive ticket system to assist players, our staff members are constantly innovating and improving the server!   
  
Questing: MassiveCraft’s RPG experience takes place in Silverwind, a colony in Essalonia. Complete quests from NPCs that lead you all around the island, fight custom mobs, solve puzzles, and become the Hero of Silverwind! You decide how the story will end.  
  
Parkour: Parkour on MassiveCraft takes place in the Gauntlet Dungeons, a long hallway built for players to traverse a multitude of physically and mentally challenging parkour obstacles which progressively increase in difficulty. Each level will grant you a unique, custom item reward on completion.', 'massivecraft.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.massivecraft.com', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'mineverso', 'Mineverso', 'Servidor actualizado y optimizado por profesionales para que puedas disfrutar de una buena experiencia sin latencia (rápida conexión).  
Actualmente podrás encontrar 5 modalidades:  
Survival, SkyBlock, SkyWars, Vanilla y CTW.  
  
