INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'mcalagaesia-mmorpg-public-build-server-looking-for-staff', 'MCAlagaesia MMORPG Public Build Server (Looking for Staff)', '**MCAlagaesia Public Build Server  
play.mcalagaesia.com**  
  
Server Website - mcalagaesia.com  
  
![](https://i.imgur.com/U3QVRJb.jpg)  
  
**Extensive Building Tutorials!**  
Visit "/warp tutorials" for a huge collection of tips and tutorials to help you improve your building skills.  
  
**Download your Plot!**  
Use the command "/p download" to download a schematic of your plot!  
  
**Minecraft Version 1.15.2!**  
Full Spigot 1.15.2 with plenty of helpful plugins from MCAlagaesia developers and others.  
  
**Huge 64 by 64 block Plots!**  
The MCAlagaesia Build Server features huge plots, four times the size of many other plot servers!  
  
**Live Map!**  
Featuring a live map of the server - explore and view your plot from above!  
Click to view the live map!  
  
**What is MCAlagaesia?**  
The MCAlagaesia Project aims to recreate Christopher Paolini''s Alagaesia in Minecraft, complete with all structures. The complete map will be hosted on a server with unique plugins that add magic, thirst and the ability to ride dragons, among other things.   
The map is based on the fantasy world of Alagaesia from the Inheritance Cycle by Christopher Paolini.  
  
**Ready to Build?**  
Join at build.mcalagaesia.com  
In order to be considered as a member of the build team, please create a medieval themed build in your plot.', 'play.mcalagaesia.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://www.mcalagaesia.com', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'apocalyptic-gaming-modpack-vanilla-network-us-eu', 'Apocalyptic Gaming Modpack/Vanilla Network [US/EU]', '![](https://apocgaming.org/uploads/4762161470cc03895d7a2307046709bd15adbbfflogo.webp)  
  
Apocalyptic Gaming Network (AGN) was founded in 2010, AGN is a multi-server modded/vanilla Minecraft network hosting 40+ servers. We host the classics as far back to MC version 1.5.2. We have strived to continue supporting every server we have ever setup. All of our plugins and server software are custom programmed. And we have custom patches for mods.  
  
We welcome everyone from any country, our servers have great latency that''s playable from any country on earth. We also have 24/7 online staff who are also international. Our goal is to provide you with the best online server experience with friendly and welcoming staff, our staff team play like normal players and we do not tolerate any form of abuse!  
  
**Features:**  
- GriefPrevention (Custom Made) & Towny  
- Economy/Shops/Rewards including Kits/Keys/Crates/Vote Rewards (Custom Plugin)  
- Dozens of worlds to explore  
- Global Chat/Mail/Messaging (Custom Plugin)  
- Active Discord Server  
- 24/7 Active Staff in game and on Discord & 24/7 Uptime  
