INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'athion-network', 'Athion Network', '**Athion Network** was crafted by the Owners of **Mithrintia** and**PI Creative** Servers to re-ignite the spark of Minecraft creativity. Both these existing servers had a solid reputation in the Minecraft community: **Mithrintia** being well known for their talented build team and **PI Creative** being one of the oldest if not THE oldest creative server around, along with being the creators of the plugin **PlotMe**.  
  
  
**Athion** was formed by four Key Members from **Mithrintia & PI Creative** (two from each server) in mid-2014 and was launched December 2014. Since then we have had our ups and downs in development but have finally set in place our top goals. With this we are achieving our goals faster than ever since our new development team **0Byte** (Zero Byte) lead by**Chamunks** has taken over the administration and development of the server.  
  
The server''s aim is to give anyone the chance to release their creativity within the game how they wish, to produce some of the best builds. We offer some of the best-optimized servers around, allowing WorldEdits in excess of millions of blocks to be executed blindingly fast. The ranking system consists of 5 ranks: Student, Apprentice, Designer, Creator, and GrandCreator. Apprentice gains full VoxelSniper and a large amount of WorldEdit, with Designer through GrandCreator gaining progressively more.  
  
If you''d rather have full access to everything, including all our special tools (listed below) then you can play in our Freebuild world, with unlimited amounts of plots, unlimited plot merging, and the ability to download your builds! You can download them with //copy then //download, or just /plot download!  
  
A few of our awesome special features!  
  
Commands:  
/ast Customize armor stands  
/cbm Customize bonemeal placement  
//center  
/compass  
//count  
//download Download a clipboard  
//fixlighting Fix pesky lighting glitches!  
/head   
/hdb Head Database  
/inv   
/mm Mirror what you''re building!  
/nv   
/place Place blocks such as 43:8  
/plot web download world Download your plot as a world file (Commission only)  
//removelighting  
//wer Make your WorldEdit region your entire plot  
  
Features:  
Punch the sky with an empty hand to open navigation menu  
Right-click a placed painting to cycle through paintings  
Fly forever with Elytra and crouch to boost  
Press Q to cycle through rows in your inventory  
  
As an entity, we aim to grow and stand out in the community both with our extensive server experience, build quality and our stand out **Build Team** that produces top of the line content.  
  
  
To find out more about us and keep up-to-date on news and new features, keep an eye on our [Forums ](http://www.athion.net/community/)and [Twitter](https://twitter.com/AthionOfficial)!', 'play.athion.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://athion.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
