INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'the-inizicraft-server-network', 'The Inizicraft Server Network', 'Inizicraft is the Server Network Built for You and Your Friends!  
  
Inizicraft is a server network that has grown and changed in its six years of existence. Inizicraft allows players to join and play along with their group of friends or collaborate with others who are on the server. We aim to provide a variety of different playing options to give all visitors something to enjoy. Rather than pay for a server or realm to play on with your friends, hop onto Inizicraft and enjoy our survival or creative worlds that provide a vanilla-centred experience, with the addition of helpful plugins that players can use if they wish. Inizicraft also hosts the Minecraft Building Toronto Network, which is a project is recreating the City of Toronto on a 1:1 Scale!  
  
Our Survival Towny Experience!  
  
Our survival server features plugins like towny and residence, which you can use to protect your builds and create thriving towns, but the game keeps its vanilla feel and doesn''t stray away from that classic Minecraft theme! Plugins like BigDoors and CMI allow the server to have an interactive building environment and a dynamic economy. Dynmap allows players to see the server''s beauty in a whole new way!  
  
Inizicraft''s rankup structure and town tournaments allow players to set goals to strive towards, while also providing their town value, and attracting new players to their towns. Ranks are available for all types of players, from builders to fighters and everything in between!  
  
The Belle Cappy Creative Experience!  
  
Belle Cappy is a community-driven city-building project where players work together to fill the island of Belle Cappy with not one, but six cities in Creative. Players are assisted with helpful plugins like WorldEdit and HeadDB to make the building experience easy and enjoyable  
  
Each region of the island has its own theme, history, and architectural style. Pick which region fascinates you and work together with others to bring it to life. The island is a place where many cultures and styles come together in an interconnected place!  
  
Home of the Minecraft Building Toronto Project!  
  
The Inizicraft Server is also home to Gamefruitpulp''s Building Toronto Project. This ambitious creative project aims to recreate the City of Toronto, Canada on a 1:1 Scale. The map features a vast and expansive cityscape that provides players with various quests they can do as visitors to get helpful items to make exploring more enjoyable.  
  
Those who are interested can also apply to be a builder on the project by completing this form: https://forms.gle/xFynzvkRXan2k9T88  
  
Learn more about our server network at http://inizicraft.net/ or check out our server hub in Minecraft at Inizicraft.net  
  
SEE YOU ON INIZICRAFT @ INIZICRAFT.NET!', 'Inizicraft.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://inizicraft.net/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
