¿A qué esperas? ¡Únete y disfruta de una experiencia única!  
  
Si necesitas ayuda o hablar con un staff, aquí tienes un enlace de nuestro discord.  
<https://discord.gg/dTFdfs4>', 'ecualia.skimdoo.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.skimdoo.com', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'rokucraft', 'Rokucraft', '**The #1 re-creation of Avatar: The Last Airbender in Minecraft featuring:**  
Custom bending, roleplaying, custom tea brewing, and hundereds of custom 3D models: Rokucraft has it all!After years and years of hard work and contribution, we are proud to welcome you to our server.   
  
In Rokucraft you can choose your bending, attend Roleplay events that involve the Avatar and others, explore the tons of recreated structures from the show Avatar: The Last Airbender. YOU will write your own story.   
  
**Features:**  
- re-creation of the Avatar: The Last Airbender world   
- new custom bending system   
- roleplay events   
- tea brewing   
- +70 new custom fish to catch and collect   
- painting your own artworks   
- minigames such as parkours   
- custom mobs   
- over hunderds of custom 3D items   
- buyable houses in villages all over the world   
... and much more!   
  
**Why Rokucraft is different from any other Avatar server(s)…**  
  
Originally created in 2011, Rokucraft now open its doors to welcome you to the server. We have so much structures that we have never shown to anyone yet waiting for you to explore. We can with confidence, say that we have one of the most accurate, detailed and immersive recreations of the world of Avatar The Last Airbender. Only 2 years ago we decided to do more with our buildings than just exploring. We have worked hard on a functionally new Bending system with own custom moves, as well as other gameplay mechanics such as tea brewing, fishing, painting and much more. We also have 3D items that make your experience unique compared to any other server.   
  
**How do you join the server?**   
  
Simply open Minecraft (1.13.2 version) and connect to the server using the ip: **PLAY.ROKUCRAFT.COM**. We have a custom resource pack so make sure your server resource packs are set on enabled! Optifine is highly recommended as it opens up a lot of possibilities to make more customization to our server such as 3D mobs and new armor.   
  
**Rokucraft is now open and playable on Minecraft 1.13.2 No mods required, though Optifine is highly recommended!**', 'play.rokucraft.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://www.rokucraft.com/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'play-performium-cc', 'Play.Performium.cc', 'Join in the first public Minecraft Among Us in Minecraft server! Play as the imposter or a crewmate. Complete tasks and win, or kill all crewmates in order to survive! Join YouTubers DoniBobes and RGA Minecraft on a server where you can get free ranks, play with youtubers, and much more!', 'Play.Performium.cc', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://www.Performium.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'wintercrest-survival-semi-vanilla', 'WinterCrest - Survival Semi Vanilla', 'IP: PLAY.WINTERCRESTMC.COM   
  
We strive to provide the best community atmosphere possible, with our thriving chat and frequent server events! What makes us different from other servers?  
  
  
For one, we are strictly against pay-to-play. ALL donor perks such as fly, speed, nick are available to all players to purchase with in game money.  
  
  
We understand how much time and effort you put into your builds and how devastating it can be to lose them. Rest assured, with our anti-grief plugins any grief or raiding will be undone and PvP is disabled! Alongside that, chests are automatically protected on placement. Alongside Relaxed Survival, we have multiple worlds for Creative & Mini-games! Here at WinterCrest - we ensure our staff members know exactly what they are doing, and have knowledgeable experience of our server. You will rank up in accordance to your helpfulness and general vibe towards your fellow players. We know that all of our staff are fair, consistent, friendly and responsible at all times.  
  
  
You can ask any staff member for help anytime. WinterCrest does not tolerate any form of staff abuse or ignorance towards players. That said, items are not spawned in and all of our staff (Including admins) play in survival. What are you waiting for? Join now!! IP: play.wintercrestmc.com Website: Wintercrestmc.com', 'play.wintercrestmc.com:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://wintercrestmc.com', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'minefield', 'Minefield', 'Vous cherchez un serveur minecraft gratuit? Qui aurait de nombreux plugins inédits, différents modes de jeu ? vous l’avez trouvé !  
  
Pionnier des serveurs minecraft francophones, Minefield a su évoluer au fil des années et des mises à jour. La communauté de joueurs soudée s''y retrouve quotidiennement (+200 000 inscrits, en hausse constante).  
  
Un incontournable de la scène Minecraft, avec de nombreux avantages ayant fait sa renommée :  
Nouveaux items et crafts vus nulle part ailleurs (+500 items et blocs).  
Système économique et de métiers  
Effectuez des quêtes uniques et journalières distribuées par des PNJ   
Events nombreux et réguliers  
Nouveaux écrans d''interface pour les joueurs : un accès à son profil, à un menu de service d’assistance.   
Un système de transport rapide et de montures personnelles  
Pas moins de 6 serveurs reliés entre eux pour un nombre total de plus de 500 slots.  
De nombreux donjons avec achievements, pour 1 à 4 joueurs !  
Des constructions et villes titanesques réalisés par les joueurs.  
Un launcher compatible pc, mac et linux.  
Serveur stable avec plus de 99% d''uptime.  
Une communauté hyperactive : vidéos youtubes, créations artistiques et éléments RP en tout genre.  
Une équipe de modération dynamique et motivée supportée par des scribes et joueurs impliqués  
Et bien d''autres que vous pouvez découvrir sans avoir besoin de vous inscrire !  
  
Minefield est précurseur et leader incontesté en France, souvent imité mais jamais égalé. Venez le voir par vous-même en téléchargeant notre client, et en vous connectant sur minefield.fr (pas besoin de créer de compte).  
Pour toute question, pour changer de rang, nous avons un forum très actif, une FAQ complète, un wiki contenant toutes les règles, et un soutien permanent sur notre mumble gratuit (connectez-vous sur minefield.fr).', 'minefield.fr', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://www.minefield.fr/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'lonksmc-towny-1-21-11', 'LonksMC [Towny] [1.21.11]', 'LonksMC is a Towny Survival server featuring MCMMO, Jobs, free rank progression, and weekly events. We focus on a friendly community, balanced economy, and long-term survival gameplay.  
  
Start your own town, build with friends, level up your MCMMO skills, earn money through jobs, complete quests, and climb through our free rank system. With regular events and an active community, there is always something to do on the server.  
  
