INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'karanteeni', 'Karanteeni', 'Karanteeni on jo vuodesta 2016 pyörinyt server, jossa pelaamisen ilo on tärkeintä. Tästä syystä emme myy peliä edistäviä ominaisuuksia, vaan niitä voit ansaita pelaamalla. Meillä saat peliajan noustessa oikeudet mm. lentoon ja ahkerimmat pelaajat pääsevät valvomaan serverin järjestystä.  
  
Karanteenissa pyörii tällä hetkellä kaksi pelimuotoa. Survival ja Creative.  
  
Survival:  
Karanteenin Survival sisältää monia parannuksia tavalliseen peliin verrattuna:  
- Voit siirtää spawnereita silk touch -hakulla.  
- Päivän pelanneena saat allesi muokattavan taikamaton.  
- Voit rakentaa hissejä emeraldblockeista.  
- Saatat törmätä itse koodattuihin mobeihin.  
  
Creative:  
Karanteenin Creativessa pyörii jo monille tuttu plotteihin jakautunut maailma.  
- Jokainen plot on 128x128 blockia.  
- Saat plotteja lisää peliaikasi noustessa.  
- Pisimpään pelanneet saavat WorldEditin käyttöönsä.  
  
Mitäs muuta voit odottaa Karanteenilta?  
- Järjestämme useita tapahtumia vuoden aikana. Esimerkkinä serverin synttäribileet kesällä tai joulukalenteri joulukuussa.  
- Iso osa serverin plugineista on itse koodattuja. Meiltä löytyy siis ominaisuuksia, joita et muilta palvelimilta löydä.  
- Kehitämme serveriä pelaajien ideoiden pohjalta. Jos serveriltä puuttuu mielestäsi jotain, voit ehdottaa muutoksia Discord-serverillämme.', 'mc.karanteeni.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://karanteeni.net/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'age-of-elysian', 'Age of Elysian', '![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/566996849509007361/567008398911078411/aoe.png)  

Welcome to Age of Elysian, a server that has been providing an immersive and feature-packed experience for over a decade. As one of the most comprehensive cracked Slimefun-Towny servers with RPG elements, we''re always adding new features to keep things fresh.  
  
Our server has many features branching into various genres and directions, so there is something for everyone. Whether you enjoy building automated mega factories, min-maxing the ultimate PvP build with stat modifiers, skills, and dungeon loot, running a world conquest as a powerful nation, or simply adventuring and doing quests, we have it all.  
  
For seasoned players, we offer many unique twists on vanilla gameplay, with new things to discover and mechanics to learn. Even if you''re new to Minecraft, almost all of our custom content is optional, so you can play the game your way and choose which parts you want to explore.  
  
Our friendly community consists of experienced players and newcomers alike. According to our statistics, over 90% of players who have clocked in over 50 hours with us never play on another server. We''re confident that you''ll love our server and be hooked from the start, so come join us on Age of Elysian and experience everything we have to offer. Who knows, we might just be the last server you ever play!  
  
![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/566996849509007361/567007760881942539/towny.png)  
In Age of Elysian, we use the popular Towny plugin to allow players to band together to form towns. With Towny, players can claim land, set roles, and grow their town from a small hamlet to a sprawling metropolis. Whether you want to compete with other towns for superiority, rally under the same banner as a Nation, or seclude yourself in a far-away corner of the map, While similar to the well-known Factions plugin, Towny is less geared towards raiding and offers a more flexible way for players to create and grow their own communities.  
  
![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/566996849509007361/567007548054568960/slimefun.png)  
Slimefun is a standout plugin on Age of Elysian, with hundreds of new items, resources, tools, and machines that expand the late-game experience and add new features along the way. With Slimefun, you''ll have fun designing and constructing your factory from the ground up, with no restrictions but your own imagination and dedication. We have customized the plugin for a more user friendly experience, as well as optimized and integrated it into the server framework for lag-free operation with even the largest megabases. There are no size limits -- our current largest factory consists of 24788 machines!  
  
![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/566996849509007361/566999189246967818/dungeons.png)  
Gather your friends and prepare for an adventure in Age of Elysian''s custom-built dungeons. These expansive and immersive dungeons offer unique challenges and puzzles for you and your party to overcome, with custom mobs created specifically for each dungeon. Defeat the bosses at the end of each dungeon to earn valuable loot, gear, and unique weapons. The difficulty level of each dungeon adapts to your party''s size and strength, ensuring that every dungeon run remains a thrilling and challenging experience.  
  
![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/566996849509007361/567006689694580748/mcmmo.png)  
A classic plugin that adds skills and abilities to the game. Train your Mining, Woodcutting, Farming, Taming, Swordsmanship, Archery, Brewing, and other half-a-dozen skills. Unlock powerful and useful abilities as you level each skill up, becoming more proficient at your trade as you gain experience.  
  
![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/566996849509007361/567004967936983070/expansivespawnregion.png)  
On Age of Elysian, the spawn region is the heart of the RPG experience. Built up over the course of many years by a number of dedicated builders, there are dungeons, towns, NPCs, quests, and beautiful sights to see. Explore and discover the world, the lore, and map out your own, unique adventure on the islands of Elysium.  
  
![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/566996849509007361/567007005210836992/muchmore.png)', 'mc.ageofelysian.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.ageofelysian.com/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'mcball-ctf-paintball-server-the-best-pvp-experience-period', 'MCBall CTF Paintball Server - The best PvP experience period', 'MCBall is a custom coded first person shooter paintball game using the Capture the Flag game mode to bring a fun, exciting experience. The combat is super-fast, high reflex shooting where one shot kills. There is a wide variety of maps with a variety of sizes and themes wspecially made for MCball!  
  
There is a variety of kits, which give you special abilities or items that can be used to your advantage. This includes kits like; Sniper with a long-range gun, Magneto which can reflect paintballs, Spider which can climb walls and trap people in webs, and many others. We have a new kit called "Richchet" that is one of a king in the minecraft universe!!!  
  
During summers MCBall holds tournaments where player formed teams get to compete against each other. The summer tournament starts soon so form up your team.', 'play.mcball.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://www.mcball.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'minevictus', 'Minevictus', 'Our server is running the latest 1.21 update with the new blocks and everything else. Were not using any form if protocol hack and were fully semi-vanilla. Minevictus is trying to bring back the old way Minecraft is supposed to be played. However, in a more modernised version.  
  
Within our server you will not find any add-ons which change gameplay. In this case we offer a stable community, polished Minecraft semi-vanilla gameplay and building tools to unleash your creativity such as the ability to draw on maps to create art and other gimmicks.', 'play.minevict.us', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://minevict.us', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'blaze-gaming-minecraft-pokemon-server', 'Blaze Gaming Minecraft Pokemon Server', 'Blaze Gaming is a Minecraft network running for over 6 years without interruption, we currently host some of the best Minecraft Pokemon game modes such as Pixelmon and Cobblemon!  
  
- [NEW] Cobblemon Infinity has been released! We have just launched our Cobblemon 1.7 server with all the latest features. Come check out our server and see for yourself what we''ve got in store!  
  
- [NOW ON 1.21] Pixelmon Storm, running on Pixelmon Reforged 9.3.14 is historically our longest running and most successful game mode, with tons of content and things to have fun with while playing Pokémon in Minecraft!  
  
▶ DISCORD : discord.gg/blaze  
▶ PIXELMON MODPACK : https://modpack.mc-blaze.com  
▶ COBBLEMON MODPACK : https://cobblepack.mc-blaze.com', 'mp.mc-blaze.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://mc-blaze.com/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'z-server-smp', 'Z Server SMP', '[Proudly Online 5+ Years] [75+ Plugins] [Dedicated & Secure] [Chill community with terrible sense of humor]  
  
