INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'safe-survival', 'Safe Survival', 'Come join the best Semi Vanilla Survival Server! Keep Inventory - SMP - Land Claims - Community! Supports Bedrock / Java Crossplay! We are a non-hub server that offers a quick start to play multiplayer Minecraft survival in a single player-like setting and run a high end server to ensure there is no lag.  
  
Number 1 Rated Semi-Vanilla Server on MCSL for over 6 years!  
  
Survival has never been easier to start, you can begin right away after walking 200 blocks from spawn or using the random teleport provided. You no longer have to worry about spawning in a massive hub or spending a half hour figuring out how to play survival. Our spawn is a very simple, but useful place filled with item shops, warps, and more!  
  
We have Grief Prevention Land Claiming, and use the additional commands spawn, sethome, and home so you can get back to your build whenever you want. Keep inventory is on.  
  
Safe Survival has a welcoming, kind, and social community. We want to provide a fun and classic Minecraft experience where you can build and explore like youre in single player. Our server is filled with the beautiful builds made by our players who will share your love for the game.  
  
Over 400000 players have joined!', 'mc.safesurvival.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.safesurvival.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'vanilla-tyme', 'Vanilla Tyme', 'New map on 8/23! Join us on 1.21.8!  
  
Vanilla Tyme is a survival server that offers a vanilla experience, with no game altering plugins.  
  
We are a whitelisted community. You must apply to play. We encourage those applying to put effort into their application.  
  
We have an active, friendly, and mature community with a dedicated staff team.  
  
- No teleporting plugin! You can travel by foot or use our expansive nether tunnels. Build and decorate your own tunnel!  
- No economy plugin! Everyone is encouraged to build a shop and compete in our trust-based diamond economy. Trade using other items too!  
- No land claim plugin! Simply find a free spot and get building!  
- No pay-to-win! Supporters are offered EULA compliant perks. Everyone is on the same level!  
- Everything is built by players, for players! You can donate materials or build alongside other members.  
- Participate in weekly events, weekly competitions, holiday celebrations, monthly build competitions, and even UHC!  
  
Our server promotes awesome builds and community; we are excited to see what you will bring to Vanilla Tyme!  
  
We have an active Discord! discord.vanillatymeservers.com  
Apply to play here : https://vanillatymeservers.com/community/apply  
Join our server here : play.vanillatyme.com', 'play.vanillatyme.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://vanillatymeservers.com', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'minelife', 'Minelife', 'Minelife is an old Minecraft server community that has been around for 11 years with players from all over the world. If you''re looking for a great place to just relax with your friends, then this is the place.  
  
