INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'vanilla-europa-smp-friendly-community-1-21', 'Vanilla Europa | SMP | Friendly Community | 1.21+', '**Java-Bedrock Crossplay Enabled! 1.21+**
  
  

**Vanilla Europa** , Europe''s most culturally relevant _Semi-Vanilla Minecraft SMP_ server since **November 2018**!   
Experience classic, community-driven survival gameplay enhanced by carefully selected quality-of-life features, all within a stable and welcoming environment.
  
  
**Player-Driven Marketplace**   
Trade items with other players at the chest-shop Marketplace, accessible via _/warp Market_!  
  
**Land-Claiming**   
Secure your builds and territory effortlessly with intuitive anti-grief features, allowing you to claim your land (_thanks to GriefPrevention_).  
  
**Player Warps**   
Conveniently share and discover player-made warps.  
  
**Proximity Chat**   
Immerse yourself in gameplay with integrated proximity voicechat, bringing a whole new dimension to your interactions and adventures.  
  
**MobHeads & Charged Creepers**   
Collect rare Mob Heads as trophies!   
Any mob or player killed by a charged creeper explosion will drop their head, and charged creepers have a unique **1% chance** of naturally spawning.  
  
**Frequent Community Events**   
Regularly hosted **HungerGames** and **UHC** events provide thrilling competitions and opportunities to earn glory and rewards.   
_It''s also twice as fun when you and your teammates have voicechat installed!_  
  
**Distant Horizons Support**   
Enjoy breathtakingly expansive render distances with smooth performance (_thanks to the DistantHorizons plugin_).  
  
**Persistent World**   
Proudly offering _no full-map resets_ since launch — your creations and legacy remain part of our server''s history.  
  
**High Mob Spawn Rates & Increased Render Distance**   
Encounter abundant wildlife and monsters for a challenging yet rewarding survival experience — all visible from afar.  
  
**Additional Features:**  
_- Enhanced item management through Minepacks (portable inventory solutions).  
- Dynamic glow effects with eGlow.   
- Powerful and user-friendly protection with GriefPrevention.   
- Rich social interactions via InteractiveChat and immersive sitting with GSit.   
- Show off creativity with customized player heads.   
- Live, interactive server map using Pl3xMap.   
- Seamless PvP control with PvP Toggle.   
- Creative market spaces via MarketManager._  
  

**Join Vanilla Europa today** and discover the perfect blend of traditional Minecraft SMP gameplay, modern enhancements, and a friendly, active community.   
_Adventure awaits!_', 'mp.vanillaeuropa.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://store.vanillaeuropa.com/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'server26-small-18-never-resetting-smp', 'Server26 - Small, 18+, never-resetting SMP', 'Join whenever...  
Server26 is a small SMP server. Only one world and everything inside build in survival. No teleports or warps, just Grief protection (Grief-prevention, etc).  
This is an adult server and looking for players 18+. We do not aim for a child-friendly environment. Aside form the rules - All things are optional and nothing is a must.  
  
The server (and thus its map) was created in 2015 and was gradually opened to the public around 2017-2018. We are located in Germany, and have players that speak German but also English.  
Recluse hermit or people person, everyone is welcome to join. One of the main ideas was it to give players a server they can return to anytime, to keep the server running no matter what, and to never reset the map. When you done looking at the buildings at spawn, you can head trough the nether to the wilderness outside the city and start mining and building on your own.  
  
We hope you give us a try and have fun!  
  
Server rules: https://server26.net/rules', 'play.server26.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://server26.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
