INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'cubedmc', 'CubedMC', 'IP: CubedMC.org  
  
You arrive at our server spawn, it’s time to explore the worlds of CubedMC!  
  
We are a PvE server. No-griefing and No-stealing guidelines are strictly enforced.  
  
💸 Earn Money:  
- 🌿 Farm Resources: Grow crops, chop trees, and mine ores and sell them to the server or player-run shops for some in-game money!  
- 🗡️ Kill Mobs: Hunt hostile mobs in the wild, or farm mob resources for funds.  
- 📜 Join Jobs: Select from jobs like Trader, Netherist, Digger, Builder, Miner, Woodcutter, Fisherman, Brewer, Blacksmith, Hunter, Beekeeper, and Farmer. The more you rank up, the more jobs you can have!  
- 💰 Create a Store: Make your own chest shops to sell goods to other players via our PlayerWarps plugin.  
  
🏛️ Run A Town:  
-Become the Mayor of a town, or join and help expand an existing community! Hermits also welcome.  
-A beginner Traveler can join a town of their choosing to get started on CubedMC.  
  
🌎 No Server Resets & Fresh Resource Worlds:  
- 🗺️ Explore a permanent 70k x 70k main world, and other worlds easily with /rtp!  
- 💎 Three resource worlds for gathering materials that reset at the first of every month!  
- 🎨 A dedicated world for map artists to build their wonderful creations.  
- 🔮 The Resource End dimension is very popular on the first of the month, so hurry in!  
  
👑 Rank Up With In-Game Money:  
-Rank up from Traveler all the way to King! Featuring inclusive titles with /male, /female, and /neutral options.  
-Unlock some unique perks, such as the use of the /workbench and the /enderchest command!  
-Explore the rank /kits as well, which provide valuable resources. Kits can be obtained daily.  
-As you rise through the ranks, you can set more homes and join more jobs.  
  
📚 Improve Your Skills:  
-Increase your McMMO power level to unlock special abilities by performing tasks!  
-Level up McMMO Abilities and Skills! The higher your skill levels, the stronger your abilities become  
  
🎮 Have Fun and Follow the Rules!  
-CubedMC has an amazing community of players and staff who are always happy to help.', 'CubedMC.org', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://cubedmc.craftingstore.net/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
