Featuring BuildCraft, IndustrialCraft, Galacticraft, and more, you can relive the golden age of automation with modern tools and improved performance.  
  
---  
  
**_The 1.12.2 Pack_**   
A large, well-balanced kitchen sink modpack with over 250 mods, designed for stability and performance.   
Explore technology, magic, and adventure in a lag-free environment with a fair economy and an active community.  
  
