RLCraft offers a challenging and realistic survival experience with over 100 mods.   
It introduces thirst, temperature, skill progression, and dangerous creatures that make survival both challenging and rewarding.   
Our optimised setup ensures smooth gameplay even in this demanding pack.  
  
