Our custom patches and plugins fix modpack issues, improve performance, and ensure a smooth, lag-free experience for every player.', 'Play.SiriusMC.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://SiriusMC.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
