INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'kilocraft-modded-edition', 'Kilocraft - Modded Edition', '**Kilocraft – Survival, Reimagined**  
  
_Vanilla at heart. Expanded in all the right ways._  
  
**Play Without Mods**  
No complicated installations! Just enter 50kilo.org in Minecraft Java and jump straight into survival, all powered by server-side Fabric mods.  
  
Kilocraft isn''t "modded chaos". The world you enter is deeper, richer, and more alive than vanilla Minecraft.  
  
![](https://i.imgur.com/zpycSlx.jpeg)  
  
**Biomes That Feel New Again**  
With [Traverse](https://modrinth.com/mod/traverse), the world gains immersive, lore-friendly biomes that blend naturally into vanilla terrain.  
  
![](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kXygSBVI/images/99dd0e60ba423c036128c21a27b9ee867b9cf165.png)  
  
Paired with [Cliff under a Tree](https://modrinth.com/datapack/clifftree), terrain generation feels more organic and dramatic. Natural cliffs, overhangs, and formations that make exploration visually rewarding.  
  
![](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/59ypHk8x/images/85dbb3571208e4822cd577bf0a8ff74f588fd67d.png)  
  
**Nether Expansion**  
With [Cinderscape](https://modrinth.com/mod/cinderscapes), the Nether gains haunting volcanic biomes, glowing vegetation, eerie atmospheres, and new survival challenges that make every portal jump unpredictable.  
  
![](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/QC4wcUXZ/images/28a1a981192c60b4a2668b7fcbc330bfeb737126.png)  
  
**The End Update Is Here**  
With [Enderscape](https://modrinth.com/mod/enderscape), the End dimension becomes a full adventure:  
  
- Multiple new End biomes with distinct terrain  
- Reworked End Cities & Strongholds  
- New mobs with unique mechanics  
- Powerful new materials and gear to discover  
- Atmospheric sounds and sky visuals that make the End feel alien again  
  
![](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/btCrWvHr/images/5fd83fb91468c27b75ffb6120240ffa0ef0652f6.png)  
  
**The World Feels Alive**  
Survival feels alive thanks to expanded mob variety.  
  
  
- [Friends&Foes](https://modrinth.com/mod/friends-and-foes) adds scrapped mob-vote creatures like Crabs, Iceologers, Mooblooms, and more.  
  
![](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/POQ2i9zu/images/e82a9ac0080130093b637ebcf6d754c684103eb0.webp)  
  
  
- [Illager Expansion Recrafted](https://modrinth.com/mod/illager-expansion-polymer) introduces new illager variants and raid threats that make villages and exploration more dangerous.  
  
![](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/zkp424MG/images/f0e7de2e9debb2c21f84be686932790f2747763f.png)  
  
  
  
- [Tom''s Mobs](https://modrinth.com/mod/toms-mobs) adds immersive creatures that fit seamlessly into vanilla biomes.  
  
![](https://i.imgur.com/Gmov6iT.png)  
  
**Automation, Storage & Base Building Depth**  
With [PolyFactory](https://modrinth.com/mod/polyfactory), survival players can build real machinery:  
  
- Conveyors & item transport  
- Mechanical presses and grinders  
- Wind-powered systems  
- Functional production lines  
  
![](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/MikpSrAF/images/2035a4db842cf939959f53b88e787dc979c1408c.png)  
  
[Extended Drawers](https://modrinth.com/mod/extended-drawers) allows massive item storage while keeping bases clean and organized.  
  
![](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/AhtxbnpG/images/8e1e419c31c7ae817e5c27601b76fe47df1b1779.png)  
  
**Survival Life, Upgraded**  
Kilocraft enhances everyday survival too.  
  
**Farming & Cooking**  
With [Farmer''s Delight](https://modrinth.com/mod/farmers-delight-refabricated), survival food becomes meaningful:  
  
- New crops  
- Cooking systems  
- Kitchen tools  
- Complex meals with real value  
Farming feels like progression!  
  
![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/456/881/kitchenware.png)  
  
[Gone Fishing!](https://modrinth.com/mod/gone-fishing) adds biome-specific fish, rare loot, and rewarding fishing mechanics.  
  
**Personalization**  
[Trimmable Tools](https://modrinth.com/datapack/trimmable-tool) lets players customize tools visually - style without imbalance.  
  
[PolyDecorations](https://modrinth.com/mod/polydecorations) adds immersive decorative blocks and furniture-style elements that help bring builds to life without overpowering vanilla style.  
  
![](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/5710VC7f/images/0745e2d3af4f5c17c2aa1c2c91ce3f00ab169665.png)  
  
With [Blockus](https://modrinth.com/mod/blockus), builders gain dozens of new block variants, without breaking the vanilla aesthetic. More palettes. More creativity. Same survival balance.', '50kilo.org', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://50kilo.org', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
