🌍 Modpack Variety: Apollo Network offers an exciting array of modpacks to cater to every kind of adventurer. Whether you''re looking for the harsh challenges of RLCraft, the boundless creativity of Divine Journey 2, or a reimagined Minecraft experience with Better Minecraft, we''ve got you covered.  
  
👫 Community-Driven: Our community is the heart and soul of Apollo Network. Join us, connect with fellow gamers, and embark on collaborative journeys, epic battles, and creative projects together. It''s not just a network; it''s a family of like-minded enthusiasts.  
  
🌐 Join the Adventure: Ready to embark on your next gaming adventure? Join Apollo Network and immerse yourself in a world of possibilities. Whether you''re a seasoned modded player or just starting out, there''s a place for you here.  
  
🌟 Why Choose Apollo Network?  
  
✅ Custom Mods and Mod Patches  
  
✅ Exceptional Performance  
  
✅ Diverse Modpack Selection  
  
✅ Thriving Community  
  
✅ Endless Adventure  
  
Don''t miss out on the fun! Join Apollo Network today and let your gaming journey take flight. Your adventure begins here.', 'rlc.apollonetwork.org', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.apollonetwork.org/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
