* Rise to the challenge of our many other in-game quests and challenges.  
* Try your hand at our upgraded vanilla fishing - custom fish, fishing quests, custom rod enchants and of course, regular fishing competitions.   
  
If you fancy a relaxed, friendly, growing community, come and spend some time here and give us a try.  
  
We are looking forward to saying hello.  
  
“Good server. Good community. Good staff”  
“I haven’t really enjoyed and Minecraft server as much as this one”  
Servers like these are very hard to find”  
  
