Bedrock IP: 67.222.153.18 Port 25566', '67.222.153.18:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://mc-ages.com', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'prismforge', 'PrismForge', 'Network Overview  
Step into a world of nostalgia reborn—our network unites many of SSundee’s classic Minecraft experiences under one roof, rebuilt from the ground up with entirely custom code/plugins. Each server delivers deep gameplay loops, modern optimizations, and community-driven features that keep you coming back for more.  
  
