- Keep Inventory is enabled  
  
  
Come Join us Today!  
play.urcommunity.net', 'play.urcommunity.net:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://store.urcommunity.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'blanktopia', 'Blanktopia', '✨ ──── Blanktopia ──── ✨  
**IP:** play.blanktopia.com  
**Version:** 1.21.4  
**Website:** [map.blanktopia.com](https://map.blanktopia.com/)  
**Discord:** [discord.blanktopia.com](https://discord.blanktopia.com)  
**Founded:** March 2020  
  
🏡 **Welcome to Blanktopia – Your New Minecraft Home!** 🏡  
Blanktopia has been a thriving, close-knit community since 2020. Whether you''re here to build, explore, or just chat with like-minded players, you’ll always find a home with us. New here? Just ask for a tour, and our friendly players will show you around!  
  
🍃 **A Relaxing Semi-Vanilla Experience** 🍃  
We blend the best of vanilla Minecraft with unique custom features to keep gameplay fresh and exciting. Our focus is on building, adventuring, and social interaction, enhanced with quality-of-life improvements and exclusive items!  
  
🏗 **Build, Roleplay & Express Yourself** 🎭  
- Unique, interactive furniture—check out **/warp ikea**  
- Buy any player head for decorating at **/warp heads**  
- Local chat & Simple Voice Chat integration  
- Sit, crawl, lay down for immersive roleplay  
- Pet your animals with a sneak + right-click!  
- Play musical instruments in-game 🎵  
  
⚡ **Quality of Life Enhancements** ⚡  
- Expanded Ender Chest (6 rows!)  
- Open shulkers, ender chests, and crafting tables directly from your inventory  
- Hide your armor or wear cosmetics with **/cos**  
- Our Resource World & Nether reset weekly, packed with custom datapacks for you to explore!  
- Smart storage – sort chests instantly, pick up items straight to inventory  
- **/search** your chests, **/store** matching items for quick organization  
  
🎨 **Custom Items & Tools** 🎨   
Unlock a whole new Minecraft experience with our powerful custom tools that make building and gathering resources fun! Some favorites include:  
- Cobalt Drill – All-in-one tool! 🔨  
- Wrench – Debug-stick magic & make invisible item frames  
- Block-Zapper – Replace blocks from a distance  
- Builder’s Wand – Place multiple blocks at once  
- Paintbrush – Recolor any dyeable block  
- Lumos – Create invisible light sources  
- Pokeball – Catch and transport any mob  
- Everstone – Keep your pets as babies forever 🐾  
- Biome Wand – Change the biomes of your builds!  
- Packing Tape – Move chests with their contents 🎁  
…and many more!  
  
🔹 **Trinket System – Unlock Special Abilities!** 🔹  
Boost your abilities with our unique Trinket System—mix and match powerful perks! Some trinkets include:   
- Grappling Hook – Press F (swap to offhand) to swing like a pro 🦸  
- Boots of Haste – Sprint even faster!  
- Horn of Plenty – Say goodbye to hunger 🍗  
- Hummingbird – Fly within your claims 🕊️  
- Booster – Hold sneak while gliding for an extra speed boost  
- Climbing Gloves – Wall jump like a ninja! 🧗  
…and many more waiting for you to discover!  
  
🛡 **Grief-Free, Stress-Free** 🛡  
Your builds are safe with our land-claim system—only give access to those you trust! No griefing, no stealing, just pure creativity and fun.  
  
💎 **Player Shops** 💎  
Our economy is entirely item based. Most players sell items for diamonds, but you can trade however you want!   
Visit **/warp shops** to explore dozens of player-owned stores!  
  
✨ **Join the Adventure!** ✨  
If you love survival, building, and making new friends, Blanktopia is the perfect place for you. Join today and become part of our growing community!  
  
📜 **Server Rules** 📜  
1️⃣ **Be Respectful** – We''re here to have fun, so be kind!  
2️⃣ **No Griefing** – If it''s not yours, don’t touch it.  
3️⃣ **Earn Your Items** – No cheats, hacks, or x-ray.  
4️⃣ **Mind Your Lag** – Keep farms compact to reduce server lag.  
5️⃣ **Staff Has Final Say** – Our friendly team ensures a fun and fair experience for everyone!  
  
🔗 **Ready to Play?** Join **play.blanktopia.com** and start your adventure today!', 'play.blanktopia.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://map.blanktopia.com/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'democracycraft', 'DemocracyCraft', '**JOIN US**  
Java  
IP: play.democracycraft.net  
  
Bedrock  
IP: play.democracycraft.net  
Port: 19132 (default)  
  
**OUR SERVER**  
DemocracyCraft is a Minecraft server that offers a unique and engaging gameplay experience, with a focus on democracy and community-driven decision making.  
  
There are a wide range of activities to enjoy on DemocracyCraft, including PvP, roleplaying, and building. Players can create their own towns and nations, engage in epic battles, or simply build and explore the world. Whatever your playstyle, you''re sure to find something to enjoy on DemocracyCraft.  
  
Here are some of the key features that make DemocracyCraft stand out:  
  
**DEMOCRACY**  
The server is run democratically, with players able to run for office and participate in government. Players can create and propose legislation, vote on laws, and even impeach officials who abuse their power.  
  
This unique gameplay mechanic allows players to have a real impact on the server''s direction and fosters a strong sense of community.  
  
**ECONOMY**  
DemocracyCraft features a robust economy system, allowing players to run their own businesses and trade with each other. Whether you''re a farmer selling crops, a miner selling ore, or a shop owner selling goods, there are plenty of opportunities to make a profit on the server.  
  
Take your business public on the share market and invest! Grow your corner shop into a multi-million dollar empire. You are only limited by your own undertakings!  
  
**CITIES & TOWNS**  
Are you ready to discover one of the most incredible Minecraft cities ever built? Introducing the City of Reveille, featuring an impressive range of districts, from the bustling downtown area to the tranquil beaches.  
  
But this city is more than just a pretty face - it''s also a fully immersive roleplaying experience, where players can explore, interact with NPCs, and experience the full range of city life.  
  
From shopping and dining to working and socialising, the City of Reveille has it all. If the city isn''t for you, then move to one of our four towns, which all boast their own themes and local governments!  
  
**CRIME**  
While DemocracyCraft is a friendly and welcoming community, it also features a realistic crime system. Players can commit crimes such as theft or murder, and law enforcement can investigate and bring criminals to justice.  
  
**COMMUNITY EVENTS**  
The server hosts a wide range of community events, including build contests, PvP tournaments, and holiday events. These events are a great way to meet other players and have fun on the server.  
  
The server has a friendly and welcoming community of players who are always willing to help out newcomers. Whether you''re looking for someone to play with or need help with something in-game, you can always find support on DemocracyCraft.', 'mcmp.democracycraft.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://www.democracycraft.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
