INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'shotbow', 'Shotbow', 'Welcome to Shotbow, the original server network!  
  
Home to the entirely custom coded gamemodes of MineZ, Annihilation, SMASH, Mine Theft Auto, and much more!  
  
No mods are required! Just connect with a Minecraft 1.12 - 1.18 client and experience Minecraft like you never have before!  
  
Originally founded in 2012, MineZ took off as one of the first vanilla Minecraft servers taking the core game that everyone knew and loved, and putting a spin on it that had never been seen before.   
  
Now, nearly a decade later, Shotbow has registered over one million unique players, and delivered quality experiences for everyone to enjoy!  
  
**MineZ - Our Origins**  
  

![](https://i.imgur.com/GnuTVb8.png)
  
  
The original Minecraft DayZ mod brought to you in Minecraft! With a beautiful hand-built map, custom Zombie AI, and many fun and challenging dungeons, there is something for everybody to enjoy!  
  
With the recently released MineZ Origins update, you will find yourself quickly immersed in the history of MineZ, and the Origins of our world. Travel and conquer the land to learn the truth behind the veil.   
  
Can you survive?  
  
**Annihilation - Defend Your Nexus!**  
  

![](https://i.imgur.com/YxrUoGd.jpg)
  
  
Are you a fan of fast paced, team based gameplay? Annihilation is the gamemode for you! Build defenses, steal the enemies resources, or take charge and destroy the enemy’s nexus before they destroy yours!  
  
With dozens of unique classes to choose from, and a multitude of different maps to experience, you will find endless amounts of engaging content to keep you coming back!  
  
Every week, four classes are temporarily unlocked for you entirely for free! Level up your in-game rank to unlock classes permanently, or alternatively purchase them in the shop!  
  
Can you be the last team standing?  
  
**SMASH - Stand Your Ground!**  
  

![](https://i.imgur.com/jcgruzn.png)
  
  
Inspired by the Super Smash Brothers line of games, SMASH is our unique take on an entirely custom PVP gamemode! Instead of trying to drop a player’s health to zero, you instead rack up a scaling knockback multiplier, eventually catapulting your opponent off of the world!  
  
Take part in SMASH Ranked, and gain as much ELO as you can to surpass your opponents, and win seasonal prizes!  
  
**Many more!**  
  

![](https://i.imgur.com/4mhx96B.png)
  
Shotbow has been around since 2012, and we pride ourselves on our suite of custom & unique games. Join us now on play.shotbow.net to see what we have to offer!', 'play.shotbow.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://shotbow.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'roleplay-hub-schoolrp', 'Roleplay Hub - SchoolRP', '![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/476120803985850368/711747061321826304/WHAT_R_WE.png)  
Looking for a roleplaying community that caters to both veteran roleplayers and new roleplayers?   
  
Then **Roleplay Hub** is the server for you! We have two main roleplays with one centering around a secondary school in Japan and one centering around the fictional fantasy world of "Enarion." Not only will you have a unique roleplay experience with us, you’ll get to see all of our amazing models and plugins!  
  
We''re a smart-minded & determined roleplay community here on Minecraft to provide the best experience possible for all of our players across all of our genres. We also provide support for platforms such as minecraft bedrock & java edition, allowing for to you play wherever.  
  
We''d be honoured to provide you with an experience to remember!
![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/476120803985850368/711741001898655804/SERVERS.png)  
  
![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/476120803985850368/711746368804487198/Untitled_design_2.png)  

  
_"Welcome to Karakura High. Where the cheerleaders are mean, jocks are stubborn and everything gets about as stereotypical as it gets.. But something here''s unique,**you**.   
  
Through what you do & the friends you make & the paths you go down - You affect not only your story but the story of **300 other active players** in the world around you._  
  
_Karakura City holds far more than meets the eye, hopefully you get a chance to discover it."  
  
__**FEATURES**_  
• An ageing system to progress through the grades!  
• Several roles to choose from once you graduate (news reporter, police officer, teacher, etc.)  
• Several clubs and sports teams to join that are run by our players  
• Purchasable (and working) vehicles and custom models!  
• Purchasable homes, penthouses & apartments!﻿  
• Working phones & attributes system to monitor your speed, stamina & lung capacity  
• And much, much more..  
  
  
![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/476120803985850368/711746033532796978/Untitled_design_1.png)  
  
Welcome to **Enarion** - a rich continent filled with intrigue, compelling stories, and sprawling Kingdoms. Seek your trade as a wandering merchant, ancient wizard, or a skilled swordsman.  
  
Forge your own destiny in a dense continent built in an immersive setting and influence the path of Kingdoms... or the continent as a whole.  
  
_**FEATURES**_  
• A comprehensive character-management plugin that seamlessly integrates multiple roleplay characters onto one account.  
• A richly detailed professions system packed with level progression, custom crafting, and unique items.  
• An innovative nation management and land-claiming plugin incorporated with Discord & Website integration as well as over a dozen other features.  
• A custom-built continent spanning over 2500 x 2500 blocks in size populated with detailed towns, ruins, and dungeons to explore.  
• The ability to forge alliances or declare wars against other nations - supported by a war system that implements large scale battles where players can utilise an array of authentic siege weaponry in real time.  
• Over 40,000 lines of custom-code to supplement many unique features and systems to enhance the roleplay experience.  
  
**![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/476120803985850368/711934112117686342/Untitled_design.png)  
  
**_"A world created only by the lengths of your imagination. We''ve taken note of the huge amount of you who have extraordinary ideas for roleplays, however - We''ve also taken note of the lack of resources a lot of you have to get things like this done._  
  
_That''s where we come in.**Roleplay Maker** allows for everyone, even the newest players to Minecraft to create their own roleplays. All from custom builds, roles, resource packs to even employing & managing your own mini-staff teams & enforcing personalised rules. _', 'mc.roleplayhub.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://schoolrp.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'castiamc', 'CastiaMC', 'CastiaMC is a server where players play an enhanced version of Survival. Players can establish their own town and create a civilization. While we have a lot of unique features to offer, our main goal is to create an enjoyable community with chill vibes only. Are you interested in joining a friendly community? This is the place for you!', 'mp.castiamc.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://castiamc.com/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'empire-war-lotr-middle-earth-castle-siege', 'Empire War - LOTR Middle-Earth Castle Siege', '_Empire War is an exciting, castle siege, PvP Minecraft server. Experience expansive class based combat, both attacking and defending locations from the Lord of the Rings novels and Films._  
  
**Each map features a new array of play-styles for you to try out and master, as well as new custom built locations to explore and discover.**  
  
Join the forces of Mordor, Isengard, Haradrim, and more evil factions. Conquer Helm’s Deep as an Uruk-Hai general, besiege Minas Tirith with hordes of trolls, or raid the fields of Edoras riding dreadful wargs!  
  
Or choose to fight for the free peoples of Middle-Earth. Defend the ruins of Osgiliath, or protect the ancient Halls of Moria! Push back the assaults on Erebor or end the evil once and for all at the doorstep of Mordor at the Black Gate!  
  
Join us, and experience firsthand the magical excitement that only Empire War can offer. Embark on a journey where you will battle, conquer, and shape your own destiny, all within a world where legends are forged: the future of Middle Earth is in the palm of your hand!  
  
Whatever you want to do, whatever side you want to fight for, Empire War allows you to jump right into Middle-Earth and feel like you’re actually part of its world.  
  
Join now with the IP:  
  
- play.empirewar.org  
  
Join our Discord server! [Empire War Discord Server [CLICK HERE]](https://discord.gg/ydvVkCX)  
  
~See you soon!', 'lotr.empirewar.org:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.empirewar.org/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
