INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'semi-survival-craft', 'Semi Survival Craft', '![](https://www.semisurvivalcraft.com/img/ssc_logo_400.png)  
  
**SemiSurvivalCraft**  
  
Welcome to [SemiSurvivalCraft](https://www.semisurvivalcraft.com)! We''re a Cross Platform Semi Vanilla Survival Minecraft server with an active community, no resets, and a whole lot more listed below! We support both Java and Bedrock version of Minecraft so you can join and play on any device. We aim to provide the best Semi Vanilla Survival Minecraft experience with a few extra protections and amenities.   
  
## Gameplay Info  
  
❇ Semi Vanilla Survival Minecraft  
❇ Multiple Sethomes  
❇ Random Teleport  
❇ Land Claims  
❇ Grief Protection *(All players can use `/co near`)*  
❇ TPA / Player Teleport  
❇ Dedicated PVP Areas *(Always protected on claimed land)*  
❇ Faster Nights when players are using Beds  
❇ Free Vote Ranks  
❇ Hard Mode Server  
❇ Large Biome Generation  
❇ No Economy Plugins  
❇ Vivecraft Supported: Minecraft VR Server  
❇ Crossplay: Java + Bedrock  
❇ No Resets *(We expand our border for new chunk / terrain generation )*  
  
## About us  
  
❇ Server Name: Semi Survival Craft  
❇ Website: https://www.semisurvivalcraft.com  
❇ Discord: https://www.semisurvivalcraft.com/discord  
❇ Server Address: `play.semisurvivalcraft.com`  
❇ How to connect: Java: https://www.semisurvivalcraft.com/#connect-java  
❇ How to connect: Windows 10 & Mobile https://www.semisurvivalcraft.com/#connect-bedrock  
❇ How to connect: Xbox & Nintendo Switch https://www.semisurvivalcraft.com/#connect-other  
❇ Versions Supported: 1.9 -> 1.21.*  
❇ Server Age: Over 4 Years online with more than 100''000 players joined!  
  
## Rules  
  
❇ Be respectful / No Excessive Vulgarity / English in public chat  
❇ No Cheats or Hacked Clients  
❇ No Excessively Laggy Builds   
*(Chunkloaders or Ultra Large farms/sorters)*  
❇ No Ads/CAPS/Spam/Racism/Politics/Religion or similar  
❇ Looting unclaimed land is allowed but griefing it is not  
❇ No TP Trap Killing (killing players after they TP to you)  
  
  
If your playing on Java Minecraft join us at **_mp.semisurvivalcraft.com_**  
  
For all other devices (Bedrock accounts, Windows 10, Mobile, Console, etc...) join us at _**mp.semisurvivalcraft.com**_ Port _**19132**_.  
  
Need Help? Join us on discord! <https://semisurvivalcraft.com/discord>  
  
Thanks for playing SemiSurvivalCraft!', 'mp.semisurvivalcraft.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.semisurvivalcraft.com/#connection-info', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
