━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━  
  
**[🌐 Website](https://softslayermc.com/) - [💬 Discord](https://discord.gg/m6ezjhJyvP) - [🗺️ Map](https://softslayermc.com/map/)**
**[📷Gallery](https://softslayermc.com/gallery/) - [❓ FAQ](https://softslayermc.com/faq/) - [📜 Rules](https://softslayermc.com/rules/)**  
  
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━  
⇒ **About Us**  
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━  
**SoftSlayer** is a Semi-Vanilla Survival server full of history that has been around for over 14 years (est. June 2011). We’re a friendly community that welcomes everybody as long as you love Minecraft! Our server is small and sweet, with the average number of players online ranging from 15 to 35. The map is permanent (no map resets, map has been live since June 2023), and there is keepInventory in the overworld. There are no P2W perks, and no land claim; we rely on the whitelist and tracking add-ons to keep your builds grief-free.  
  
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━  
⇒ **Features**  
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━  

- Player-run shops on our SoftSlayer Market. The economy is diamond-based to counter spooky scary hyperinflation  
- Build Contests with different themes and amazing rewards in our specialized creative world  
- Resource world with up to date features from the latest MC update  
- Death Valley: Endgame, high-risk high-reward custom PvP arena with stronger mobs and periodically respawning loot chests  
- Library full of books written by our players since 2012, accepting all aspiring writers!  

  
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━  
⇒ **Rules**  
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━  
We''re not asking much rules-wise, just no griefing, stealing, cheating or harassing others. Our main goal is to host a chill environment where our players can relax and be themselves. Those against this idea will quickly find themselves looking for a new server ;)  
  
Join us today by applying in our **[Discord](https://discord.gg/m6ezjhJyvP)**! The application is very simple, just some questions to help us gauge the kind of player you are, and if you would be a good fit for SoftSlayer. Hope to see you online!', 'softslayer.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://softslayermc.com/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
