Welcome to 🌸 BlossomCraft 🌸, an excellent server known for it’s amazing experiences. We are a laid-back, no grief, economy, SMP server where we value community above all else. The server is running 1.21+, and everyone is welcome as both Java and Bedrock players are free to join!   
  
