INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'feather64', 'feather64', 'About feather64  
feather64 has been operating since 2011. We created the server after some of our favorite servers closed and we were unable to find the same game style. We are a Raiding-Survival server with very little moderation. We allow raids, PVP, and griefing. On feather64 you cannot protect/claim land. We have a clans system, an economy system which uses Lapis Lazuli, and basic commands like sethome and tpa. Play your way on feather64. Grief and raid, hide and collect, design and construct, enchant and pvp, it''s up to you.  
  
Rules  
  
1. Do not use macros, or hacked clients. QOL mods are allowed.  
2. Do not use duplication glitches which work on all items. Dupes which work on one item are allowed.  
3. Follow the directions of admins and mods. Directions given to other players do not apply to you.  
  
  
Most of our active players are located in North America however all are welcome. Many of our players are friendly and supportive however because we provide very limited moderation, you may find some toxic players. You are able to use type "/ignore " for anyone that bothers you. We have an active Discord server for feather64. Discord is where we give out important information about the server. You''ll find voice channels with active players and text channels with memes etc. If you join the Minecraft server and decide to stick around, please join the discord. You will not be able to send messages or join voice channels on the discord server until you link your Minecraft account to your Discord account.', 'feather64.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://feather64.net/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'justysurvival', 'JustySurvival', 'Justy Survival Server - Staff Needed See Below  
Full Server Release 16/01/2021  
  
Bored of standard Survival? Want to play with friends and not get bored? Join our brand new fully customised Survival Server today! - JustySurvival!  
JustySurvival is a Survival Server Like No Other, with so many custom mods & active server developments! There is tons to do on our EPIC server! Grab your friends, start a base and build together!  
  
Key features:  
▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬  
We are a sponsored Survival server with a Twitch Affiliate - Justy135:  
➤ Land Claiming - Claim land & live with friends  
➤ MCMMO - Level up Sword, Axe, Mining, fishing Skills! etc.  
➤ Economy - Grind money by killing mobs or Questing.  
➤ Player Trading - Trade with others securely.  
➤ Chest Locking - Use a sign to lock chests and keep people out!  
➤ Gates - Build a castle with a HUGE gate, open and close it to let people in/out!  
➤ Stream Events - Custom Events streamed by Justy135.  
➤ PVP - Kill someone and steal their head to hang in your base!  
➤ Leaderboards - Compete with others to be the richest!  
➤ Player Shops - Run the economy with your very own shop!  
  
➤ IP: play.JustySurvival.com (Server is now LIVE)  
➤ Discord: https://discord.gg/a6AYTSv  
➤ Website/Store: https://justysurvival.enjin.com/  
▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬  
  
Staff Needed:  
With the new release of our Server - we of course need some staff! Positions below:  
DO NOT - Join and demand a rank.  
  
Moderator - Moderate the server, help new players.  
Builder - Building custom builds i.e. Spawn, PVP arena .  
Graphic Designer - On hand to design graphics when needed.  
Video Editor - Create video for promotional purposes.  
Website Helper - Help building our Enjinn Website.  
Plugin Developer - Help get the best Plugins developed for the server.  
  
  
Thanks for viewing - See you in there!!', 'play.justysurvival.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://justysurvival.enjin.com/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
