**Music Pack:** The server features beautiful, custom music that requires a manual download from: https://www.avatarmc.com/wiki/rp', 'avatarmc.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://avatarmc.com', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
