INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'prismacraft', 'PrismaCraft', '🌎 _**About PrismaCraft:**_  
At PrismaCraft, community always comes first! Whether you''re building your own thriving town, climbing the leaderboards with skills, or mastering lucrative jobs, PrismaCraft has something for every type of player.Our active and friendly staff consistently roll out updates and enhancements. Join our Discord to be part of our thriving community, discuss new features, and suggest your ideas!  
  
🏠 _**Towny Features (1.21.4):**_  
**Towny Land Claiming** - Create your dream town – whether it''s a solo farming empire, bustling city, or cozy community with friends!  
**Skills & Progression** - Level up 15 unique skills, gaining stat points to enhance stats like health, defense, attack, and unlock powerful bonuses.  
**Jobs & Player Economy** - Choose from 12 rewarding jobs—mining, fishing, building, and more—to steadily grow your wealth. Our economy is entirely player-driven, allowing endless opportunities!  
**Dynamic Seasons** - Experience changing seasons every week, affecting temperature, environment, and gameplay bonuses (minimal negative effects—engage only as much as you''d like!).  
**Custom Mobs** - Encounter 20 unique mobs and over 50 exciting new fish species. Capture them and bring them home!  
**Custom Enchants** - Over 100 unique enchantments to customize your gear, available through enchanting tables and special traders.  
**Craftable Gear** - Forge unique armors, tools, and powerful talismans. Equip specialized weapons like scythes, daggers, great axes, and spears, each with distinctive abilities!  
**Resource Worlds** - Fresh worlds reset monthly, brimming with custom ores, plants, and valuable loot!  
**Custom Fishing** - Catch and collect nearly 100 unique fish!  
**Alchemy** - Discover rare recipes to craft potent potions, enhancing your power for intense gameplay moments.  
**And Much More!** - PrismaCraft''s expansive systems mean endless fun and possibilities. Join us in-game or on Discord—we’re excited to guide you through all we have to offer!  
  
🎨 _**Creative Features (1.20.4 - 1.21.4):**_  
**Powerful Building Tools** - Get instant, unlimited access to Axiom, World Edit, Voxel Sniper, goBrush, goPaint, and detailed armor stand editing tools.  
**Earn Free Ranks** - Participate in events to unlock extra creative plots and special perks!  
**Fun Cosmetics** - Progress through ranks and earn amazing cosmetics like disguises, customizable player sizes, and hats!  
**Upload Schematics** - Seamlessly upload and continue your builds from other servers or single-player worlds using World Edit schematics.', 'play.prismacraft.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://wiki.prismacraft.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
