INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'omniverse-network', 'Omniverse Network', '🌎 Welcome to Omniverse  
  
A one-of-a-kind Minecraft experience with four fully-developed game modes, each packed with custom content and unique progression systems:  
  
🌤 SKYBLOCK  
Build your island, conquer custom challenges, and rise through the ranks.  
100s of quests and an expansive mining cave with regenerating ores, loot chests, and combat mobs  
A deep fishing system with 100+ custom-textured fish that can be caught as you progress  
Infinite island sizes, island upgrades, and a reputation system with your island companion, Frank  
Competitive and Casual profiles with monthly payouts for those playing competitive  
  
🪐 PRISON  
Mine your way through the galaxy with a fully custom prison experience  
Custom in-house pickaxe plugin with upgradeable backpacks and enchantments  
25+ planet-themed mines, 26 ranks, and 25 prestiges – each with its own rewards  
Personal cells with upgradeable expansions  
Mob arenas, mining bombs, and an in-depth fishing system with 100+ custom fish  
  
🎨 CREATIVE  
Let your creativity run wild on massive plots.  
WorldEdit and Voxel access (unlockable for free)  
Download your builds anytime  
Endless building possibilities  
  
⚔ KITPVP  
Fast-paced PvP with a twist.  
Unique economy-based PvP system  
Kill players for money, create and store custom kits, and dominate the leaderboard  
Team up or go solo – the choice is yours', 'mp.omni-verse.us', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.omni-verse.us/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'ecosmp', 'EcoSMP', '**Genuine Community | Free /fly In Claims | In-Game Ranks | Towns/Nations | Balanced Economy | Player Shops | Custom Jobs | Semi Vanilla | Discord Integration | No Server Resets | Cross-Platform**
  
  
**Built for the Long Run**  
  
EcoSMP is a cross-platform semi-vanilla survival server built around long-term, well-balanced gameplay and a genuine community. From the start, the goal has been simple: create a server that is fun to play, safe to be part of, and worth investing your time in for the long run.  
  
We care deeply about the quality of both the server and the community behind it. EcoSMP is intentionally family-friendly, welcoming, and held to high standards, with a focus on maintaining a smaller, higher-quality community rather than chasing numbers. We want the server to feel respectful, trustworthy, and enjoyable for the people who call it home.  
  
**An Economy That Matters**  
  
As the name suggests, **EcoSMP** is also built around economy. The economy is not just a side feature here — it is a core part of the server’s identity. It is **action-based** , **player-driven** , and carefully balanced so that progression feels earned and money has real value. Whether you are building, trading, working, expanding a town, running shops, or progressing through ranks, there is always something meaningful to do and something worthwhile to work toward.  
  
**What You Can Do**  
  
On EcoSMP, you can earn money through unique gameplay, progress through in-game ranks, create towns and nations, level custom jobs and unlock rewards, build and run player shops, collect custom items, use free /fly in town claims, stay connected with Discord integration, and play on a world with **no server resets**.  
  
**Why EcoSMP**  
  
EcoSMP is designed for players who want more than a temporary server or a shallow grind. We are building a long-term home with strong values, rewarding gameplay, and a community that people can genuinely feel good about being part of.  
  
If that is the kind of Minecraft server you have been looking for, we would love to welcome you to EcoSMP.', 'play.ecosmp.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://docs.ecosmp.net/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
