INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'joyncraft', 'JoynCraft', '**Welcome!**  
  
Joyncraft is a VanillaPlus paper server using Multiworlds to provide two separate worlds to play in. Bedrock players can joyn us, too!  
  
PvP only with consent!  
  
**COMMUNITY**  
Our community members are mostly adults, many of them have known each other for years, with the occasional kid mixed in, some of them members of our own families. We''re all pretty chill people who know how to entertain ourselves in a game with endless possibilities. Everyone is welcome as they are. Just be respectful and you''ll feel right at home.  
  
**VOTE RANKS**  
Voting regularly unlock new ranks, which give you access to quality of life features and bonuses like extra claim blocks and of course a fancy Tag to your name in chat. No pay to win here, you can unlock it all just by being part of our community and voting for our server.  
  
Two worlds:  
**SURVIVAL WORLD**  
is on HARD MODE, has a QuickShop economy, with an option to get your builds moved over to BUILD WORLD if you want to keep them forever. The survival world keeps things fresh and exciting for everyone.  
The End and Nether will be partially reset regularly, the other half of them is open for farms and builds.  
  
**BUILD WORLD**  
is on EASY MODE and grants every player access to creative mode, if they so desire, but you can also play survival mode, or just occasionally pull some materials out of creative that you don''t feel like grinding today.  
The build world never resets. It''s the best place if you just want to relax and build away, without being limited by small plots in a boring flatworld. Here our experienced staff members can help you out with WorldEdit features like mirroring or copy/pasting.   
  
Our separate worlds exist to give everyone options without having to go to a different server every time. If you don''t like "cheating items" in creative, but your buddy hates grinding, you can be in the same server now and still both play it however you like.  
  
**Joyn Joyncraft today and make yourself at home! We are looking forward to getting to know you!**', 'Joyncraft.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
