INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), '8-builders-8-tools', '8 builders 8 tools', '8b8t was created in early 2021 and has been online for over a year. As of February 17, 2022, the map is over 2000 Gigabytes in size and there are over 148 thousand unique player joins in 8b8t. The server was originally created after Leee''s main server at the time, also known as 6b6t, was backdoored and removed by a close friend of his. 8b8t is pretty much the original 6b6t but renamed and better in almost every way.  
  
It is a server that has an average of 50 to 100 players. It''s a server where you can do whatever you want following the only 3 rules: no spam, no crashes, no lags. It can be played in both versions of Minecraft Java and Bedrock. The server is located on a computer owned by the owner Leee.', '8b8t.me:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.8b8t.me/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'aryntius', 'Aryntius', '« Introduction »  
  
Halfway between Dark Souls and Diablo 2 comes Aryntius--a new take on the classic loot-based RPG system chock full of strange unique items, challenging bosses, and complex tilesets for you to discover and conquer on your way to build the strongest character.  
  
« About the Server »  
  
The primary focus is to explore and overcome massive, sprawling dungeons full of treasure, tough monsters, and challenging bosses while gaining incredible gear, accessories, and other items to help you on your journey.  
  
Optionally, there is also enhanced Survival available--where you are free to explore dozens of custom biomes in a 10k-wide custom-generated world, build massive bases or tons of outposts conveniently with an ease-of-access shop and an obscenely-high home limit, or create/join a guild and make yourself be known!  
  
Notably, Aryntius is designed around intense combat with an extremely high difficulty level. The server is ill-suited for players that desire relaxing, casual roleplay.  
  
« Features »  
  
- Tons of items and gear to craft and loot (over 1000+ new items!)  
- Multiple dungeons with branching pathways and secrets  
- Guns, bombs, and other explody things  
- Magic, spells, and similar arcane studies  
- Unique bosses to fight and defeat  
- Backpacks to expand your storage space  
- Incredibly diverse and wild land generation  
- Over 9000 /sethome positions  
- And much, much more!  
  
« Vote Rewards »  
  
- 10,000 Sigmas (In-game currency)  
- 1,000 Runes (Can be exchanged for unidentified items)  
  
« Other Info »  
  
- Website: www.aryntius.net  
- Discord: discord.gg/juu8r9P  
- Server IP: play.aryntius.net', 'play.aryntius.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://aryntius.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
