Graylist Server w/ New Player Anti Grief Timer  
  
We strive to improve our server for our active community. Everything in-game is designed in mind for you to always have something you can do: roleplay, crafting, resource gathering, exploring, and more.', 'potp.rpdnd.com:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://rpdnd.com/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
