INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'bayanihan', 'Bayanihan', '𝐁𝐚𝐲𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐡𝐚𝐧  
"Uniting Filipino Minecrafters".  
  
𝐕𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧  
to provide every Minecrafter a safe haven where they can fully enjoy the game with mature players.  
  
𝐀𝐛𝐨𝐮𝐭 𝐮𝐬  
Bayanihan started during the Covid-19 Pandemic Era. The server first started as a realm because I wanted to still have the ability to roam during the lockdown. The server has faced different turmoil which caused it to turn on and off. It was only then that I fully understand what was missing and why I keep failing as a server owner.  
  
𝐓𝐡𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐜𝐚𝐧 𝐝𝐨  
𝓟𝓵𝓪𝔂 𝓢𝓜𝓟 - Enjoy a simple SMP feeling where there''s a very minimal restriction of what you can''t do. We don''t use plots in this server and fully rely on a rollback plugin to restore damages and punish offenders. By doing this, we are able to develop trust and instate discipline in the community.  
𝓓𝓮𝓼𝓲𝓰𝓷 𝓲𝓷 𝓒𝓻𝓮𝓪𝓽𝓲𝓿𝓮 - Our Creative mode is very simple where you can just focus on designing your future builds for the SMP mode.  
𝓦𝓲𝓷 𝓪 1𝓿1 - Since a lot of my players love PVP, I added a 1v1 PVP mode where you can join a queue of pvpers and claim your way to the ranks.  
𝓔𝓷𝓳𝓸𝔂 𝓪 𝓒𝓪𝓻𝓷𝓲𝓿𝓪𝓵 𝓻𝓲𝓭𝓮 - We have a Carnival mode that opens every weekend where you can spend your hard-earned diamonds and enjoy awesome rides that give you a very immersive experience.  
𝓕𝓲𝓰𝓱𝓽 𝓓𝓾𝓷𝓰𝓮𝓸𝓷𝓼 𝓑𝓸𝓼𝓼𝓮𝓼 - I have added Dungeons in order for the players to still have something to do during the late game phase of the SMP. You can get unique skins from Dungeons to pimp your tools and weapons.  
𝓗𝓸𝓻𝓻𝓸𝓻 - Play Horror maps where your sanity will be greatly tested.  
𝓜𝓲𝓷𝓲𝓰𝓪𝓶𝓮𝓼 - Need a break from grinding in SMP? Well, we have a Minigames mode where you can have fun with other players.  
