INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'crimson-club', 'Crimson Club', 'Gamemodes:  
- Survival  
- Oneblock Tycoon  
- Crystal PvP  
  
  
Crimson Club is an Indonesian server for versions 1.16.5 - 1.20.6. Its a survival genre based server with custom RPG Items, as well as Dungeons and Boss Fights to help give a new gaming experience. Interested in finding out what else you will find on the Crimson Club Minecraft server? Check out the list of features below.  
  
