We believe that players should be able to play the game as they see fit, which is why we have a strict no-banned items policy. We want you to enjoy the full potential of the modded Minecraft experience.  
  
At Mystian Fields, we also take server backups and snapshots regularly, ensuring that your progress is always safe and secure. Our staff is friendly and always willing to help, making your gaming experience all the more enjoyable.  
  
Join us today and discover all that Mystian Fields has to offer!  
  
Join our Discord to find specific pack versions', 'play.mystianfields.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://discord.gg/D2cabqkU3m', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'us-playcdu-mechanical-mastery-plus', '[US] PlayCDU | Mechanical Mastery Plus', '![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/455359036540321804/975393973931769916/Banner.gif)  
  
