INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'silvermons', 'Silvermons', '![](https://i.ibb.co/nkpSNbL/Silvermons-Banner.jpg)  
  
**Silvermons** is a non pay-to-win friendly community server network including Pixelmon and Cobblemon. Both servers have a custom level cap and rank progression system that includes our exclusive Gyms and Elite 4. The Pixelmon server additionally has the Conqueror’s Castle, Master’s Gauntlet, and Legend’s Spire. Beyond these progression systems, the Pixelmon server has content for players of all interests. This includes our Weekly Tournaments with multiple formats, group based content like Dungeons, repeatable Battle Tower, Noble 6 and Endless Waves, unique Player Gym system, Fun Events, and more! The Cobblemon server also has many of these features and will soon have all of them. We also have all 1025 Pokémon, all gimmicks, and many other unique systems to explore!  
  
• Server IP: **play.silvermons.com**  
• Pixelmon Reforged on Minecraft 1.16.5 and Cobblemon Fabric on Minecraft 1.21.1  
• Modpack: The Pixelmon Modpack (https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/the-pixelmon-modpack)  
• Modpack: Cobblemon Official Modpack [Fabric] (https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/cobblemon-fabric', 'play.silvermons.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'cobbleland', 'CobbleLand', 'Discover Your Perfect Cobblemon Adventure on CobbleLand!  
  
Welcome to our Cobblemon community, where we celebrate the diversity of playstyles and preferences! Our unique network of servers is designed to cater to every type of Cobblemon enthusiast, ensuring that you find your ideal gaming environment. Whether you seek thrilling battles, peaceful exploration, or an entirely new Cobblemon experience, we have a server just for you.  
  
No matter which server you choose, you''ll be part of a vibrant and welcoming community of Cobblemon enthusiasts. Participate in community events, collaborate with fellow players, and share your adventures, creations, and strategies. Our servers are more than just gaming platforms; they''re places where friendships are formed, and shared passions thrive.  
  
Here is a short list of some of the features that we have on our server:  
