Our Server IP: play.cobbleland.com', 'play.cobbleland.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://store.cobbleland.com/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), '18-terra-nova-kingdom', '[+18] Terra Nova Kingdom', 'Hear Ye, Hear Ye, One and All! 📣  
  
Do you seek a new begining? Do you fancy an exciting adventure? 🏰  
  
Draw Forth and Join the Ranks of Terra Nova, A Vanilla Survival Server! (18+) 🌍 Our 1.20.1 server is once again recruiting players from all corners of the earth to join our amazing community. We are an 18+ only community, and cater to those ages.   
  
Rise up the ranks from lowly Peasant to sceptered Knight, all the while enjoying the foison that the server can offer thyself! Explore the beauty of the Shopping District, Server hosted Tournaments and Events, and enjoy the many plugins our Server has to offer. 🧙‍♂️   
  
🔒 Protect thy crown jewels with Bolt! (Container Protection)  
🗺️ Explore the Realm with DynMap! (Live Map)  
🪑 Rest thy weary head with GSit! (Sit, Lay Commands, etc.)  
🔐 Fear not for thine Home and Kin with CoreProtect! (Block Logger)  
🛡️ Hide thine Armor from scoundrels with Hidden Armor!  
👛 Enjoy the Shopkeepers and City-Mannered folk! (Shop NPC’S and Custom NPC’S)  
  
We are a purely community server. We are catered to your enjoyment and do not sell roles, ranks or benefits on the server. We are a free to play community that aims at bringing creative players together and foster a community that lasts.   
  
Join us to create memories that last a lifetime. Our dedicated moderator team and a plethora of friendly players will make your journey on our server fun and exciting. Team up with other players, progress through ranks based on play time and explore the far reaches of Terra Nova today!   
  
Wait, do not forget to participate in our incredible player driver economy! Build your magical store in our Shopping District, amassing richness beyond your wildest dreams.   
  
To join, simple press on our discord server invite link! https://discord.gg/4atd4qyYhh  
We cant wait to see you join our beloved Terra Nova! Be not a Candle-waster, but a King in thine own Castle and Join our Community Today! 🤴🏰', 'play.terranovasmp.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://www.terranovasmp.net', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
