• Boss Fights, PvP Events & Seasonal Rewards   
• Active Staff & Discord Support   
  
[hr]  
  
**💎 Progression Path:**  
1️⃣ Start in Tutorial World   
2️⃣ Build in Plot World   
3️⃣ Grind in Survival World   
4️⃣ Raid in Adventure World   
5️⃣ Earn glory and climb the leaderboard!  
  
[hr]  
  
