• **Version:** 1.21.3+   
• **IP:** play.khmerkpc.com   
• **Discord:** [Join our community!](https://discord.gg/yourlink)   
• **Website / Store:** [store.khmerkpc.com](https://store.khmerkpc.com)   
  
[hr]  
  

**✨ Join KhmerKPC Today! ✨**
  

_No cheats. Just skill, teamwork, and Khmer pride._
  

**Build your legend — in the land of Yggdrasil!**
  
  
![](https://yourimageurl.com/footer.png)', 'mc.khmer-kpc.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://khmer-kpc.tebex.io', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
