INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'nexly-network-super-craft-bros', 'Nexly Network | Super Craft Bros', 'Nexly Network is the original recreation of SethBling and Minecade''s classic gamemode, Super Craft Brothers.  
  
Featuring 60+ unique characters on 30+ different maps, fight using fast paced double-jumping and abilities of each class to survive until the end!   
  
This gamemode is a faithful recreation of Minecade''s now closed down gamemode. Before Mineplex and Hypixel, this was Minecraft''s #1 server and was home to THOUSANDS of different players.  
  
This gamemode is a 1.8.9 PVP gamemode but is available to play on the current Minecraft version!  
  
For further info, check out Nexly Discord server. Send a message and say hello!  
https://discord.gg/6t2W8NENep', 'nexly.network', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://nexly.network', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'back2basics-1-smp', 'Back2Basics #1 SMP', 'We are a brand new survival server with completely custom plugins and a fresh map for our players to begin adventuring on.  
Every player has access to a randomtp so you can find the perfect spot to start your adventure!  
Other awesome features include:  
Keep inventory  
24/7 server uptime  
Active owner/admins  
If you have any questions at all feel free to join our discord and ask!!  
Thank you for your time!', 'mp.back2basics.gg', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://discord.back2basics.gg', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'lumamc', 'LumaMC', '⭐ Welcome to LumaMC! ⭐  
If you''re on the lookout for a new Minecraft server that has a beautiful feature set and tight-knit community, look no further!  
  
🎉 Our features:  
  
🏘️ Towny - Establish and grow your own town, forming alliances and building a community! We also use Towny as our main claiming system! Join other players towns or nations to build friendships!  
  
🪙 mcMMO - Level up your skills and become a true master of your craft.  
  
⚒️ Custom Items - Enjoy our custom coded items that have special abilities and unique skills!  
  
💰 Player Economy - Engage in resource gathering, production, and trade to influence supply and demand dynamics!  
  
📈 Ranks System - Climb the ranks to earn different titles and abilities.  
  
🎨 Artmap - Express your creativity with map designs and make your mark on the server!  
  
🍂 Dynamic Seasons World - Watch as the world transforms based on the season! Times of day and weather syncs up to real life! (Northern hemisphere)  
  
🐠 Fishing Competitions & Custom fishing - Test your fishing skills and compete for glorious rewards! Fish from fishing competitions are also custom!  
  
👷 Jobs - Work jobs to earn cash and make your way up the ranks and purchase materials, items, furniture, or anything else!  
  
🌎 We have an extensive roadmap featuring thrilling content updates and events that will keep you on the edge of your seat.  
Your feedback matters! We encourage our community to share their thoughts, ideas, and suggestions. LumaMC is not just a server; it''s a collaborative space where every player plays a vital role in shaping our community.  
  
Join us and become part of a community that values creativity, fun, and enjoyable memories.', 'play.lumamc.net', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://lumamc.net/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'kalifate-craft', 'KALIFATE CRAFT', 'SMP focused on peaceful economic gameplay.  
  
Economy? Money? How do I earn it?  
  
Jobs. We all know our classic /job in most SMP servers, so we also have it too. We will be providing features for it in the future.  
  
AutoSellChest, this classic feature that we love, automatically sells items you''ve farmed, harvested, or collected! Sells it automatically to the shop in-game, so be creative with how you make your money!  
  
Quarry Machines to automatically harvest resources, utilized on farms or mob farms to earn money in-game.   
  
We developed our own plugin six months ago, providing a command-less gameplay experience that focuses on exploration, survival, and what to explore.   
  
Phone: This in-game item can''t be dropped or lost unless you leave it in a chest. The phone introduces convenience to things like /rtp /shop & many more features to come.   
  
We also offer a Non-PVP World where you and your friends can survive. But watch out, as you never know when we''ll release a horrible mob at night.   
  
PVP? Weapons?   
  
All of the above. We''ve provided an arena for players to test their PVP skills on! As for custom weapons, we want the community to decide what weapons we should release. We make our own weapons, so it stays unique to what we hold. We don''t buy models.  
  
  
Overworld Features:   
  
Realistic Season. Make sure you stay warm by crafting leather armor.  
  
GriefPrevention. Prevents mobs and players from griefing your home or creation.  
  
CustomFood. Releasing more of them soon.', 'klf.tkza.tekkura.cloud:2002', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://discord.gg/78RhCRHfCf', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'archmc', 'ArchMC', 'ArchMC is one of the biggest servers in North America with gamemodes designed for every play style. Founded by a team of Minecrafters, our server has become the go-to for anybody seeking a new experience and a fresh breath of gameplay. Whether you''re into Minigames, Hardcore Survival, or Creative plots, there''s something for everyone here. Join today and Rule Your Own Game.', 'arch.mc', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.arch.mc', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
