INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'albionmc', 'AlbionMC', 'Welcome to AlbionMC - Where Fantasy Meets Minecraft!  
  
*18+ Server* Apply on AlbionMC.com  
  
History:  
Albion was only a thought a few years ago as a pandemic rocked the world and everyone stayed home and needed to figure out how to fill in their time.  
A group of friends met up each day and spent their free time playing on a minecraft server called TownyClassic.net that we all loved.  
A few years later the world restored itself back to normal and everyone went back to work.  
As time went on players faded from the server we played on and one day it just... vanished. We lost everything we built and contact with alot of the amazing people we met along the way.  
At that point we were devistaed and thats when we thought of the idea to make our own Minecraft server to ensure that this would never happen again.  
During this time we played on another server and it fell too, and it just kept being a curse to us. Finally we all got together on New Years Eve and decided what we all wanted and how we wanted this to roll out.  
We have been working hard every momemt trying to make Minecraft... Minecraft again. We want to add new things we have never seen and provide a great space for a new type of community.  
We promise that AlbionMC will continue thoughtout the ages! We never want anyone else to feel the dissapointent we felt ever again.  
  
  
Our Server:  
We have over 50 plugins in our massive mmo fantasy world, with a amazing spawn to start your journey with useful perks and features.  
As you play you can gain ranks by typing /rankup to give you new gear and extras to help you start your world. You can start your own town and protect all your items within. Invite friends or simply show off using the dynamap plugin from anywhere!  
The world was generated on Minecraft v 1.21! We are one of the first servers to start with this massive updated version. Finally our servers are located in the North East of the United States - EST  
  
Embark on an Epic Adventure  
Dive into a world where magic and imagination collide with Minecraft.  
Join AlbionMC.com, a fantasy-themed Minecraft server where every block tells a story, and every adventure brings new discoveries.  
  
Join Our Community  
Become part of an 18+ vibrant community of adventurers, builders, and storytellers.  
Share your tales, collaborate on projects, and forge friendships that transcend the boundaries of the digital realm.  
Our dedicated staff ensures a welcoming environment where every player''s voice is heard.  
Trying to make friends as an adult we have personally found to be a difficult feat. We hope our world will help create lasting friendships all across the world!  
  
Begin Your Adventure Today  
Are you ready to embark on a journey that defies imagination? Join AlbionMC and experience Minecraft as you''ve never seen it before.  
Whether you seek riches, fame, or simply the thrill of discovery, your destiny awaits in our enchanting world.   
Connect with Us  
  
Server IP: albionmc.com  
Discord: https://discord.gg/ksRsVMHgTD  
  
Stay updated on the latest news, events, and updates  
  
Experience the Magic - Apply to Albion MC Today!', 'AlbionMC.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://www.AlbionMC.com', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
