✅ ALL 1025 Pokémon (no fakemons, no missing mons)  
  
🐉 Legendaries, Mythicals & Ultra Beasts spawn  
  
💥 All Mega Evolutions (including Mega ZA)  
  
⚡ Mega, Dynamax, Gigantamax, Terastallization, Z-Moves  
  
