🗼 Weekly tournaments with massive prizes  
  
🛡️ Level 1–100 Battle Pass  
  
🎯 Global bounty system (become the #1 Poke Hunter)  
  
💪 Custom EV/IV training systems  
  
🔎 PokeNav to track spawns  
  
  
🌍 Two Unique Regions  
