🧢 100+ cosmetics (Shiny Sylveon Hat, Kyogre Sword & more)  
  
🧸 2,000+ collectible Pokémon plushies  
  
🐣 Advanced daycare breeding  
  
💎 Weekly Shiny Saturday boost  
  
  
⚔️ World Events & Bosses  
💥 Alpha bosses with rare loot  
  
🌑 50+ custom Shadow Pokémon  
  
✨ Daily / Weekly / Monthly quests  
  
🍛 Pokésnacks to boost shiny odds, catch rate & friendship  
  
  
🛠 Performance & Quality of Life  
