🏆 Ranks: Level up through in-game ranks to unlock unique perks and rewards!  
⏰ Playtime Rewards: Earn exciting rewards based on your playtime levels.  
🎉 Monthly Events: Join in on fun, engaging events every month!  
⚔️ MCMMO: Train and level up RPG skills to enhance your gameplay experience!  
👥 Dedicated Staffs: Our dedicated staff members are always here to help and ensure a great experience!  
🌈 Join us on Cozy Realms and find your perfect balance of fun, relaxation, and community! ✨', 'play.cozyrealms.us:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://store.cozyrealms.us/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'your-crafts', 'Your Crafts', '🌿 Welcome to Your Crafts SMP – A New Era of Survival Begins!  
  
Looking for a Minecraft server that captures the magic of exploration, survival, and progression — without losing the soul of classic gameplay? Your Crafts SMP is where medieval fantasy meets carefully crafted mechanics to deliver a deeply immersive, player-driven world.  
  
⚔️ What Makes Us Different?  
  
🧭 A Living World, Lore-Rich and Expansive: From humble beginnings as a Wanderer, climb your way through a deep rank system inspired by medieval roles — earn your place as a Oracle, with custom kits, unique perks, and server-spanning influence.  
  
🏰 Claim, Conquer, and Grow: With the Lands plugin, manage your own territory, form alliances, go to war, or build thriving communities. Whether you’re a lone homesteader or a proud nation leader, you decide your path.  
  
🛠️ Custom Jobs & Professions: Level up with Jobs Reborn using custom-made roles like Alchemist, Blacksmith, and Tamer — each with a hand-built economy and reward system that respects your time and creativity.  
  
💎 Balanced Economy & Player Shops: Trade smart with ChestShops, balanced pricing, and a server-wide market built by real players. Everything has value — from rare artifacts to freshly caught fish.  
  
📜 Immersive RPG Touches: Titles, lore-driven messages, progressive kits, and meaningful survival challenges — with McMMO, CMI, and other light enhancements to make everything feel just right.  
  
🎮 No Whitelist. No Discord Requirement. Just Pure Survival. Jump in and start your journey. Whether you''re in it to build, explore, lead, or trade — there’s a place for you here.', 'mc.yourcrafts.us:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://yourcrafts.us', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'vexlaris', 'Vexlaris', 'The Vexlaris Minecraft Server is a family-friendly, all-ages 13+ community that focuses on survival gameplay. Hosted by my streaming discord brand name Vexelab, Vexlaris offers a rewarding and safe environment for players who enjoy working together, exploring, and building in a vibrant and dynamic world.  
Key Features:  
  
CMI: CMI manages the economy, server essentials, and commands, with added features such as custom portals for travel between worlds.  
  
Grief Prevention: Players can claim and protect their land, ensuring builds are safe from unwanted griefing.  
  
AngelChest: When a player dies, their items are stored safely in an AngelChest, allowing them to retrieve everything without the stress of losing their valuables.  
  
Jobs Plugin: Players can take on jobs to earn money and experience points, which help them rank up and unlock new perks.  
  
TreeAssist: This handy plugin lets players quickly fell entire trees, making resource gathering faster and more efficient.  
  
LushRewards: Random rewards are distributed as players engage with the game, keeping things exciting and offering incentives for regular play.  
  
DiscordSRV: Integrates the Minecraft server with the Vexelab Discord, enabling communication between platforms and syncing player roles.  
  
Dynmap: An interactive web-based map of the server, allowing players to view the world in real-time and navigate more easily.  
  
Resource World: A separate resource world is available for mining, where players can gather resources freely. This world will be periodically reset to keep the main world focused on building.  
  
Warps: Players can use warps to quickly travel to select areas, including shops and specific biomes in the resource world.  
  
Voting: Players can vote for the server to increase its exposure while earning rewards. There are future plans to introduce a crate plugin with a voting crate and three other tiered crates.  
  
Vexlaris continues to evolve, with exciting updates and community-driven improvements on the horizon to enhance the survival experience.', 'mc.vexelab.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://www.vexelab.com/vexlaris-mcserver/vexlaris', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
