INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'delphicraft', 'DelphiCraft', 'Mythic Survival | Custom Skills | Land Claim | Ranks | Adventure  
  
DelphiCraft isn''t just a Minecraft server; it''s a decade-long odyssey of creativity, community, and adventure. As one of the oldest continuously operating Minecraft servers, we''ve been crafting unforgettable experiences since 2012. Our tight-knit community welcomes both seasoned players and newcomers alike to become part of our ever-unfolding story!  
  
IP: playdelphi.com  
Bedrock IP: mc.playdelphi.com (19132)  
Discord: https://discord.gg/2BbV34jUDT  
Founded: 2012  
  
🏛️ Embark on an Epic Journey 🏛️  
  
DelphiCraft offers a unique blend of Ancient Greek mythology and steampunk innovation, providing a playground for your imagination. Whether you''re erecting grand temples to the Olympians or tinkering with bronze automatons, there''s a place for every builder and dreamer here.  
  
⚡ Key Features ⚡  
  
- Unique Theme: Ancient Greece meets Steampunk  
- Long-standing Legacy: Over 10 years of continuous operation  
- Safe Haven: A quiet, protected space for your creations  
- Time Travel: Access to all historic worlds in Adventure mode  
- Up-to-date: Fully compatible with the latest Minecraft releases  
- Community-Focused: Tight-knit group of friendly players  
  
🛠️ Quality of Life Enhancements 🛠️  
  
- Chest and inventory sorting  
- Toggle Phantoms and PvP  
- Land claiming and protection  
- Player shops  
- Backpacks for extra storage  
- Auto-load/unload items to nearby chests  
- Auto-eat from inventory  
- AngelChests to safeguard your items upon death  
- Custom skills and vote-based ranks  
  
🏺 A Living Museum of Minecraft History 🏺  
  
Unlike other servers, DelphiCraft offers a unique glimpse into Minecraft''s evolution. Explore our historic worlds, each a snapshot of Minecraft''s past, preserved in Adventure mode. From our humble beginnings to our current grandeur, witness the growth of not just a server, but a community.  
  
🛡️ Build with Confidence 🛡️  
  
Your creations are sacred to us. Our robust land protection system gives you complete control over access and permissions to your builds. With regular off-site backups and a fault-tolerant system, your masterpieces are safe for eternity.  
  
🧙‍♂️ Supported by Technical Wizardry 🧙‍♂️  
  
Our team of experienced staff keeps DelphiCraft running smoother than Hermes'' winged sandals. With 99% uptime and swift response to support requests, you can focus on what matters most - your Minecraft adventure.  
  
🌟 Our Community Promise 🌟  
  
At DelphiCraft, we believe in:  
  
- Fostering a welcoming environment for players of all ages and backgrounds  
- Preserving your creations across the ages  
- Balancing vanilla gameplay with quality-of-life improvements  
- Celebrating creativity and collaboration  
  
🎭 Join Our Epic Tale 🎭  
  
In DelphiCraft, every player is a hero in their own odyssey. Will you rise as a master architect, shaping grand coliseums? Perhaps you''ll delve into the mysteries of redstone, creating marvels that would impress Hephaestus himself. Or will you be the nexus of our community, forging bonds as strong as Celestial Bronze?  
  
Your legend awaits in DelphiCraft - join us in writing the next chapter of Minecraft''s longest-running epic!', 'playdelphi.com:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://www.playdelphi.com', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
