INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'tetrabearmc', 'TetrabearMC', '**TetrabearMC** [SMP] [Semi-Vanilla] {1.21.4} {SE Asia} {Greylist} {Economy} {Crossplay} {16+}
  
  
![](https://static.planetminecraft.com/files/resource_media/screenshot/14311091-banner_lrg.jpg)  
  

**SERVER INFO**
  
  
**Server Version:** Java Edition 1.21.4   
**Server IP (Java):** **play.tetrabear.xyz**   
**Server IP (Bedrock): play.tetrabear.xyz, port 25669**  
**Server Location:** Singapore  
  
**Dynmap:** <http://map.tetrabear.xyz>   
**Website:** <https://tetrabear.xyz>   
**Subreddit:** /r/TetrabearMC   
**Instagram:** <https://instagram.com/tetrabearmc>  
  

**About Us**
  
  
Hello! We are a long-standing survival server with a strong focus on **building a close community within Southeast Asia**. Players from all over the world are welcome however! We recently just gone through a **new world reset** for a new season! For this season, we also opted to use custom terrain generation through the Terralith data pack for a fresh experience. Gameplay is still vanilla SMP however!  
  
Our players usually focus on making **great builds** , participating in **server events** , trading in our **player-driven economy** , or just **hanging out**! We typically draw players from the Philippines, Singapore, India, Malaysia, and Indonesia!  
  
We also have a [**Discord**](https://discord.gg/46AJcJ4dQP) and our subreddit /r/TetrabearMC that serve as **hubs for our community** outside the server.  
  
Come check out our world as well on our [**Dynmap**](http://map.tetrabear.xyz).  
  

**MEMBERSHIP**
  
  
**Anyone is free to connect to the server but in order to build and play, you must be a whitelisted member first.**  
  
Membership is done on our [Discord server](https://discord.gg/46AJcJ4dQP). Look for the "rules" and "how-to-join-mc" channels. Please read through them carefully as we are strict on enforcement on these rules.  
  

**MAIN SERVER FEATURES**
  
  
* **Terralith Custom Terrain**. We chose this terrain generator since it doesn''t mess much with vanilla gameplay while also providing something fresh.  
* **QuickShop** plugin. Fully featured player economy and chest shop system!   
* **Anti-grief through action logging**. All players are able to view the CoreProtect logs through the [code single]/inspect[/code] command.  
* **Chests can be protected** by right clicking (without sneaking) it with a sign.  
* **You create a grave when you die**. No more worrying if you can get your stuff back!  
* Instead of waiting for all players to sleep to skip the night, **the night moves faster the more players sleep**. The tick speed also speeds up during this, so your farms will have a better chance to grow!  
* **Shulkers have limited respawns at end cities**. No need to go out so far to get new shulker shells!  
* **The Ender Dragon drops elytra on death**. So elytras are more accessible!  
* **Two-way chat with in-game and our Discord!**  
* **Extra Achievements to pursue** with BlazeandCave''s Advancements Pack. Makes gameplay more rewarding!  
  
_Three Spawn System_  
One of the unique features we are trying out this season is the 3-spawn system. Rather than everyone starting at the same spot, you choose one of 3 places to start your journey on the server. This also becomes your only warp/home location to teleport to. You are free to change your warp/home location any time by visiting the other spawns, and to make this easier there are already pre-built highways connecting them!  
  
We put this system to hopefully encourage players to build closer and collaborate more without feeling like the central location is getting crowded.  
  

**MAIN RULES**
  
  
1. **Be respectful** to all players, their belongings, and their builds. Griefing and stealing will be dealt with accordingly.  
2. **Be mindful** of your language. Swearing is allowed, but offensive remarks and spam are discouraged.  
3. **Be responsible** with your play. Hacking and cheating are grounds for a ban.  
  
**There is a ZERO-TOLERANCE policy on all griefing, stealing, and hacking. Committing any of these will cause you to lose your membership without warning.** More detailed rules are on our Discord  
  
We hope to see you around!', 'play.tetrabear.xyz:25581', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://tetrabear.xyz', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
