・Besides staff and players we’re always looking for advice how to improve the server.  
・Discord: discord.pokemasters.org  
  
🔗 Server IP: play.pokemasters.org', 'play.pokemasters.org', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://shop.pokemasters.org/', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'dungeoncraft', 'DungeonCraft', 'Dungons, Loot, Grindy, Grind, Brainrot, Op, Fun, Minecraft, Grind through exciting dungeons and farm loot! Gathering loot will power you up to progress to the next dungeon! Find ULTRA RARE Void item drops to aid you on your journey! Grind our VOID currency and purchase free DONOR RANKS in /ranks. See you there! BRAND NEW UPDATE EVERY DAY!  
  
