Join MineWars now and prove you have what it takes to conquer the battlefield! 🏆⚔️🔥', 'minewars.minecraft.vodka:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
