🪣 Infinite Water Bucket – Endless water for your builds.   
🧽 Everydry Sponge – Dry out areas instantly.   
🌾 Replanting Hoe Enchantment – Auto-replant crops.   
🔥 Molten Touch Pickaxe Enchantment – Smelt ores as you mine.   
📋 Community Board at Spawn – Advertise shops or services.   
🐾 Give Pets to Others – Share pets with /givepet .   
📦 Show Items in Chat – Display gear with [item] and [inventory].  
  
⚡ NEW: mcMMO Skill System  
  
🎯 Level up skills like Mining, Fishing, and Combat.   
💪 Earn abilities and perks as you play.   
🧱 Balanced to enhance survival gameplay.  
  
🛡️ Resetting Resource Worlds  
  
