INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'smash', 'Smash', 'Welcome to the Ultimate SMASH Server!  
  
Are you ready for the ultimate showdown in Minecraft? On our brand-new SMASH server, you’ll experience thrilling matches, epic battles, and nonstop action! Whether you’re already familiar with the game mode or just looking to try something new, this is the perfect place for both fun and competition.  
  
What is SMASH?  
  
SMASH is inspired by the famous Smash Bros games from Nintendo and has been lovingly adapted into a 3D Minecraft world. The goal is simple: hit your opponents as often as possible. Every hit increases your % value – the more you accumulate, the further you’ll be launched off the map. Who will survive the longest? Who will become the ultimate champion?  
The game mode combines fun and strategic depth: you can casually play with friends or prove your skills in intense, competitive matches. Perfect for anyone who loves action, precision, and timing.  
  
About Our Server  
  
Our new, custom SMASH plugin offers a wide range of features to make every match exciting:  
• Many diverse maps to battle on   
• Numerous items for tactical combat   
• Party system to play matches with friends   
• ParticleTrails for unique visual effects   
• KnockoutSounds for epic finishing moments   
• Classic scoreboard system for familiar gameplay   
• Regular updates and bug fixes   
  
And the best part: our server is playable on all Java versions from 1.20.2 onward. Whether you’re an experienced player or just starting out, there’s a place for you here. Our team is small but dedicated, and we welcome every player ready to dive into SMASH.  
  
Interaction & Support  
  
Got ideas, suggestions, or found a bug? No problem! Use the in-game commands /support or /bugreport to contact our team directly. We’ll handle your requests as quickly as possible.  
  
Other useful commands:  
• /dailyreward – Claim a free reward every day   
• /party – Create parties with your friends   
• /ping – Check your connection to the server   
• /ptime – Set your own in-game time   
• /spectate – Watch your current match   
• /stats – View your personal statistics   
• /quit – Safely leave an ongoing match   
  
Premium Without Real Money  
  
Right now, it’s possible to earn premium rank or extras without spending real money! Enjoy features that are usually reserved for paying players.  
For the latest updates, events, and community news, join our Discord:  
  
Discord: https://discord.gg/JwUT2jFJHX  
  
Come see for yourself and dive into the world of SMASH – we can’t wait to see you in action! Have fun fighting and surviving on our server!', 'supersmash.eu:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://discord.gg/JwUT2jFJHX', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
