INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'statecraft', 'StateCraft', '**JOIN US**  
Java  
IP: play.statecraft.net  
  
Bedrock  
IP: play.statecraft.net  
Port: 19132 (default)  
  
**OUR SERVER**  
StateCraft is a Minecraft server that offers a unique and engaging gameplay experience, with a focus on democracy and community-driven decision making.  
  
There are a wide range of activities to enjoy on StateCraft, including PvP, roleplaying, and building. Players can create their own towns and nations, engage in epic battles, or simply build and explore the world. Whatever your playstyle, you''re sure to find something to enjoy on StateCraft.  
  
Here are some of the key features that make StateCraft stand out:  
  
**DEMOCRACY**  
The server is run democratically, with players able to run for office and participate in government. Players can create and propose legislation, vote on laws, and even impeach officials who ***** their power.  
  
This unique gameplay mechanic allows players to have a real impact on the server''s direction and fosters a strong sense of community.  
  
**ECONOMY**  
StateCraft features a robust economy system, allowing players to run their own businesses and trade with each other. Whether you''re a farmer selling crops, a miner selling ore, or a shop owner selling goods, there are plenty of opportunities to make a profit on the server.  
  
Take your business public on the share market and invest! Grow your corner shop into a multi-million dollar empire. You are only limited by your own undertakings!  
  
**CITIES & TOWNS**  
Are you ready to discover one of the most incredible Minecraft cities ever built? Introducing the City of New Hamilton, featuring an impressive range of districts, from the bustling downtown area to the tranquil beaches.  
  
But this city is more than just a pretty face - it''s also a fully immersive roleplaying experience, where players can explore, interact with NPCs, and experience the full range of city life.  
  
From shopping and dining to working and socializing, the City of New Hamilton has it all. If the city isn''t for you, then move to one of our four towns, which all boast their own themes and local governments!  
  
**CRIME**  
While StateCraft is a friendly and welcoming community, it also features a realistic crime system. Players can commit crimes such as theft or murder, and law enforcement can investigate and bring criminals to justice.  
  
**COMMUNITY EVENTS**  
The server hosts a wide range of community events, including build contests, PvP tournaments, and holiday events. These events are a great way to meet other players and have fun on the server.  
  
The server has a friendly and welcoming community of players who are always willing to help out newcomers. Whether you''re looking for someone to play with or need help with something in-game, you can always find support on StateCraft.', 'mcmp.mcstatecraft.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'http://mcstatecraft.com', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
