INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'infinity-isles', 'Infinity Isles', 'Who Are We?  
  
Infinity Isles is a Semi-Vanilla, Discord Whitelisted, 18+ community server that started its 2nd Season in March 2025. We are a community focused server with some plugins to help with quality of life and multiplayer fun while keeping what makes vanilla special!  
We are a mature and respectful server who are based on trust, honesty and transparency. There is always a friendly face around or someone willing to help if you need it. It doesnt matter what your game/experience level is, as long as your mature 18+ and respectful, you belong here 😀  
  
What Makes Us Stand Out?  
  
🍦 SEMI VANILLA: We are a primarily vanilla survival server with come quality of life changes like proximity voice chat and dynmap  
  
🔒 WHITELISTED: We review every application to make sure that only the best players join our community! Rest assured, trolls, and immature players are not welcome here. Our staff team will promptly handle griefers, and any damage they may cause is swiftly rolled back and repaired.  
  
🌎 SERVER LOCATION: We are hosted on the East US coast to ensure good connection and reachability for players all around the world.  
  
🛒 SHOPPING DISTRICT: Infinity Isles has its very own player-run shopping district with themed shops that let players show off their creativity! All based upon a diamond economy (you can always find a diamond somewhere to spend)  
  
🐻 EVENTS: We have a variety of events being organised by both the Staff Team and members of the community. We are always welcome to new ideas or helpers to make the events even more awesome.  
  
⛏️ RESOURCE WORLDS: We have special-made portals at spawn leading to resource worlds, for all three dimensions; overworld, nether, and end! Here you can gather large quantities of materials that would otherwise ruin areas, and help us keep our regular worlds neat! It’s also great for finding un-looted structures! These worlds are reset monthly to get new areas and to refresh the damaged landscape from all your mining needs.  
  
⚒️ COMMUNITY BUILDING: The server common areas like the Spawn, Shopping Districts and Games are all built with the community. We hold build competitions for major features/builds and work together to see these come to life while remaining in survival.  
  
💸 NO PAY-TO-WIN: Donation perks are strictly non-P2W to ensure every player has the fairest experience. All proceeds go directly towards improving server performance as the server continues to expand and grow each week. There are a few options each with their own set of commands, some include nicknames, CustomDiscs, Head Database, a wide range of cosmetics, and more. You can browse our donation options at infinityisles.tebex.io/.  
  
🔧 STAFF: Our team of friendly staff are always around and are here to help you if you need a hand and help foster a non-toxic, relaxing and safe community for all to enjoy!  
  
👾 DISCORD: We have an active community over on Discord regularly chatting in channels and in voice chats!  
Join us today! Apply in our discord: [url]https://discord.gg/t8NNN6tZvd[url]', 'mc.actuallyod.in:25565', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
