INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'elysium-smp', 'Elysium SMP', '🌌 Welcome to Elysium  
  
A one-of-a-kind survival experience built for every playstyle.  
  
Whether you’re a master builder, a redstone genius, a fearless survivalist, a competitive PvPer, or just here to hang out and make friends — Elysium has everything you need to thrive.  
  
🔹 What Is Elysium?  
  
Elysium is a challenging yet rewarding survival world where your potential has no limits.  
  
Want to dominate the economy? Go for it.  
We actively encourage creative ways to earn, trade, and spend — with countless systems designed to support your grind.  
  
And the features? There are too many to list.  
  
Ride on the back of an Ender Dragon, soaring across the skies.  
  
Drive cars across the land.  
  
Fly planes above the world.  
  
Discover mechanics that will make you say, “I didn’t even know a server could do that.”  
  
If you can imagine it — there’s a good chance it exists here.  
  
📜 LORE  
  
Long ago, the Fallen Gods walked this world as its guardians.  
Their power shaped the seas, forged the mountains, and bound life itself together.  
  
But pride turned to war… and war to ruin.  
  
One by one, the gods fell — some slain, some vanished, others sealed beyond time — leaving behind only echoes of their power.  
  
In their absence, the world began to wither.  
The land cracked. The skies grew restless.  
Ancient evils stirred where divine light once stood watch.  
  
Relics of the gods remain scattered across the realms — blades, tomes, forgotten temples — each carrying fragments of power that could either doom what remains… or restore it.  
  
Now the world stands on the brink of collapse.  
  
Not waiting for gods to return —  
but for heroes to rise.  
  
The fate of this world no longer rests in divine hands.  
  
It rests in yours.', 'elysiumsmp.xyz', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
