INSERT INTO servers (id, slug, name, description, host, port, game, status, online_mode, region, website_url, discord_url) VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'thronecraft-legends', 'Thronecraft: Legends', '![](https://i.imgur.com/Qg1B6sn.jpeg)  
  
_
**Thronecraft: Legends – A Legacy Reforged**
_   
  
No respawning. No second chances. In Thronecraft: Legends, every decision matters because your character’s life is their only one.  
  
We combine immersive roleplay with the most interactive combat system you’ll find in Minecraft Roleplay. Battles are fluid, skill-based, and unforgiving.  
  
But survival isn’t the only story worth telling. Our world is a sprawling medieval fantasy setting where politics, faith, and ambition collide. Whether you’re a farmer, mercenary, or noble, every choice you make will ripple across the realm. Friendships and rivalries carry weight, cities rise and fall, and wars are fought not just with steel, but with words and willpower.  
  
_
**What Makes Us Different**
_  
  
● **One Life, One Legacy:** death is permanent. Every lethal duel, every battle, and every betrayal has true consequence.  
  
● **Intuitive Combat Mechanics:** a custom-built system that makes fighting dynamic, skill-driven, and immersive.  
  
● **A Living World:** explore a hand-crafted medieval fantasy setting in Varith shaped by players, politics, and storytelling.  
  
● **Player-Driven Narratives:** your character’s choices and story directly shape history and influence the realm.  
  
● **Tight-Knit Community:** we value mature, dedicated roleplayers who want authentic stories, not grindy RPG loops.  
  
_
**Server Details**
_  
  
**IP Address:** play.thronecraftrp.com   
**Version:** 1.20.4  
  

**Join Thronecraft: Legends today and step into a world where every action, every duel, and every word could define – or end – your legacy.**', 'play.thronecraftrp.com', 25565, 'mc_java', 'active', true, NULL, 'https://discord.gg/xc9xgVJ7Ej', NULL) ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
